var book = {
	"name": "Yosua",
	"numChapters": 24,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE akoa Mose wuo akyiri no, AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Nun ba Yosua, Mose somfoɔ no sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> M’akoa Mose awu; afei sɔre twa Yordan yi, na wo ne ɔman mu yi nyinaa nkɔ asase a mede merema wɔn, Israelfoɔ, no so.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Baabiara a mo nan bɛtia no, mo na mede mama mo, sɛdeɛ meka mekyerɛɛ Mose no,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ɛfiri serɛ no so ne Lebanon yi ho de kɔsi asu kɛseɛ no, Asubɔntene Eufrate ano, Hetifoɔ asase nyinaa de kɔsi ɛpo kɛseɛ no ano wɔ deɛ owia kɔtɔ hɔ na ɛnyɛ mo hyeɛ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Obiara biara rentumi nnyina w’anim, wo nkwa nna nyinaa; sɛdeɛ medii Mose akyire no, saa ara na mɛdi w’akyire; merempa wo na merennya wo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Wo ho nyɛ den na yɛ nnam, na wo na wobɛkyɛ asase a mekaa wɔn agyanom ntam sɛ mede bɛma wɔn no mu ama ɔman yi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Wo ho ara na ɛnyɛ den na yɛ nnam pa, na hwɛ di mmara a mehyɛɛ m’akoa Mose no nyinaa so; mfiri ho nkɔ nifa anaa benkum, na deɛ wobɛkorɔ nyinaa woadi yie.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Mma mmara nwoma yi mmfiri w’anomu, na dwene ho awia ne anadwo, na woahwɛ ayɛ sɛ deɛ wɔatwerɛ no wɔ mu nyinaa teɛ no: Na ɛno na wo kwan bɛyɛ dwoodwoo, na ɛno na ɛbɛsi wo yie.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Menhyɛɛ wo sɛ yɛ den na yɛ nnam, nsuro, na mma w’akoma nntu anaa? Ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE wo Nyankopɔn di w’akyi deɛ wokorɔ nyinaa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛnna Yosua hyɛɛ ɔman no ahwɛfoɔ no sɛ:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Momfa nsraban no mu, na monhyɛ ɔman no sɛ: Monsiesie akwansoduane nsie, na ɛha yi nnansa morebɛtwa Yordan yi akɔfa asase a AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn de rema mo sɛ monni soɔ no.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ ne Manase abusuakuo fa no deɛ, Yosua ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Monkae asɛm a AWURADE akoa Mose hyɛɛ mo sɛ: AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn de mo atena ase, na ɔde asase yi ama mo;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> mo yerenom, mo mma ne mo mmoakuo ntena asase a Mose de maa mo Yordan agya yi so, na mo deɛ, monni mo nuanom anim amia mu, akofoɔ nyinaa, na monni mmoa wɔn,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> nkɔsi sɛ AWURADE de mo nuanom bɛtena ase sɛ mo, na wɔn nso wɔbɛdi asase a AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn de rema wɔn no so ansa na moasane aba mo sodie asase no so abɛdi so, sɛ AWURADE akoa Mose de maa mo, Yordan agya owiapueeɛ hɔ no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na wɔbuaa Yosua sɛ: Deɛ woahyɛ yɛn nyinaa, yɛbɛyɛ, na baabiara a wosoma yɛn no, yɛbɛkɔ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Sɛdeɛ yɛtiee Mose, ade nyinaa mu no, saa ara na yɛbɛtie woɔ; die na AWURADE wo Nyankopɔn nni w’akyire, sɛdeɛ ɔdii Mose akyire no.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Obiara a ɔbɛte w’anomu asɛm ho atua na ɔrentie wo nsɛm, deɛ wobɛhyɛ yɛn nyinaa mu no, wɔnku no. Den ara nko na wo ho nyɛ, na yɛ nnam."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Nun ba Yosua somaa mmarima asrafoɔ baanu firi Sitim ahuntaeɛ mu sɛ: Monkɔ nkɔhwɛ asase no ne Yeriko. Na wɔsii mu kɔe, na wɔduruu ɔbaa dwamamfoɔ bi a wɔfrɛ no Rahab fie, na wɔdaa hɔ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na obi kɔka kyerɛɛ Yeriko hene no sɛ: Hwɛ, mmarima bi a wɔfiri Israelfoɔ no mu aba ha anadwo yi rebɛsra asase yi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Yeriko hene no soma maa wɔkɔɔ Rahab nkyɛn sɛ: Yi mmarima a wɔaba wo nkyɛn na wɔabɛhyɛne wo fie no firi adi, na wɔbaa asase yi nyinaa nsra.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔbaa no faa mmarima baanu no de wɔn huntae; na ɔkaa sɛ: Ɛwom, mmarima no baa me nkyɛn deɛ, nanso mennim deɛ wɔfire;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na esum duruiɛ a wɔrebɛto kuro pono no mu no, na mmarima no firii adie; mennim deɛ wɔkorɔ. Monti wɔn ntɛm, na mobɛto wɔn.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔno deɛ, na ɔde wɔn akɔ ɛdan atifi na ɔde wɔn akɔhunta ɛsowa a ɔde aboa ɛdan no atifi no ase.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na mmarima no tii wɔn faa Yordan kwan so de kɔɔ atwaeɛ; na wɔn a wɔtii wɔn no firii adie ara pɛ, na wɔtoo kuro pono no mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na wɔn deɛ, wɔnnya nkɔdaeɛ no, ɔbaa no foro kɔɔ wɔn nkyɛn ɛdan no atifi",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> kɔka kyerɛɛ mmarima no sɛ: Menim sɛ AWURADE de asase yi ama mo, na mo ho hu atɔ yɛn so, na asase yi sotefoɔ nyinaa akoma tu mo anim.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na yɛate sɛdeɛ mo Misraim fire mu no AWURADE maa Mmɛwa Po mu nsuo wee wɔ mo anim ne deɛ moyɛɛ Amorifoɔ ahemfo baanu a wɔwɔ Yordan agya no, Sihon ne Og a mosɛee wɔn pasapasa no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na yɛteeɛ no, yɛn akoma tuiɛ, na home bi rensɔre bio obiara mu wɔ mo anim, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn no, ɔno ne Onyankopɔn wɔ nyameso ɔsoro ne asase so ɛfam.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na afei monka me AWURADE ntam sɛ, sɛ mayɛ mo yie yi, mo nso mobɛyɛ m’agya fie yie, na momma me nokorɛ nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na momma m’agya ne me na ne me nuammarimanom ne me nuammaanom ne deɛ wɔwɔ nyinaa nnya nkwa, na monyi yɛn mfiri owuo mu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na mmarima no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Yɛn kra nsi mo ananmu nwu, sɛ woanka yɛn asɛm yi ankyerɛ, na ɛba sɛ AWURADE de asase yi ma yɛn a, yɛne wo bɛdi no adɔeɛ ne nokorɛ so.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ɛnna ɔbaa no de ntampehoma twetwee wɔn faa mpomma mu sisii fam, na na ne dan si kuro no ho fasuo so, na ɔfasuo no so na ɔteɛ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Bepɔ so na monkorɔ, na atifoɔ no anto mo, na monhunta hɔ nnansa nkɔsi sɛ atifoɔ no bɛsane, na ɛno akyiri no moakɔ mo kwan.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na mmarima no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Yɛbɛdi bem afiri ntam a womaa yɛkaeɛ yi ho.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hwɛ, sɛ yɛreba asase yi so a, fa asaawa kɔkɔɔ homa yi kyekyere mpomma a wode yɛn faa mu sii fam no mu. Na boa w’agya ne wo na ne wo nuanom ne w’agya fiefoɔ nyinaa ano wo nkyɛn wɔ efie ha,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na obiara a ɔbɛfiri adi afiri wo fie pono ano akɔ abɔntene soɔ no, ne mogya bɛgu n’atifi, na yɛn deɛ, yɛadi bem; na obiara a ɔwɔ wo nkyɛn efie no, sɛ obi de ne nsa ka no a, ne mogya ngu yɛn atifi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na sɛ woka yɛn asɛm yi kyerɛ a, ɛno nso yɛbɛdi bem afiri ntam a womaa yɛkaeɛ no ho.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔkaa sɛ: Ɛnyɛ sɛdeɛ mo nsɛm yi teɛ. Na ɔgyaa wɔn kwan na wɔkɔe; na ɔde homa kɔkɔɔ no kyekyeree mpomma no mu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛnna wɔsii mu kɔduruu bepɔ no soɔ, na wɔdii hɔ nnansa kɔsii sɛ atifoɔ no saneeɛ. Na atifoɔ no hwehwɛɛ wɔn ɔkwan no so nyinaa, nanso wɔanhu wɔn.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na mmarima baanu no siane firii bepɔ no so, na wɔtwa baa Nun ba Yosua nkyɛn, na wɔkaa deɛ ɛyɛɛ wɔn nyinaa kyerɛɛ no,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> na wɔka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Ampa ara, AWURADE de asase no nyinaa ahyɛ yɛn nsa, na afei nso asase no sofoɔ nyinaa akoma atu wɔ yɛn anim."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ɛnna Yosua sɔree anɔpahema, na wɔtu firii Sitim, na wɔduruu Yordan ano, ɔno ne Israelfoɔ nyinaa, na wɔdaa hɔ ansa na wɔretwa.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na nnansa wiee duro no, ahwɛfoɔ no kyinii nsraban no mu,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> kɔhyɛɛ ɔman no sɛ: Sɛ mohunu AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn apam adaka no ne Lewifoɔ asɔfoɔ a wɔso no a, mo nso montu mfiri deɛ mowɔ, na monni akyire;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> nanso monsusu ɔkwan bɛyɛ sɛ basafa apem nto mo ne no ntam, mommmɛn no, sɛdeɛ ɛbɛyɛ na moahunu kwan ko a mobɛfa soɔ, ɛfiri sɛ momfaa ɔkwan yi so pɛn.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ ɔman no sɛ: Monte mo ho, na ɔkyena AWURADE bɛyɛ mo mu anwanwadeɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ asɔfoɔ no sɛ: Monsoa apam adaka no nsene nni ɔman no anim. Na wɔsoaa apam adaka no dii ɔman no anim.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Ɛnnɛ da yi na mɛfiri aseɛ mayɛ wo kɛseɛ Israel nyinaa ani soɔ, na wɔahunu sɛ, sɛdeɛ medii Mose akyire no, saa ara na mɛdi w’akyire.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na wo deɛ, hyɛ asɔfoɔ a wɔso apam adaka no sɛ: Sɛ moduru Yordan nsuo no ano a, monnyina Yordan mu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ Israel mma no sɛ: Montwe mmra ha, na montie AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn nsɛm.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛnna Yosua kaa sɛ: Yei na mode bɛhunu sɛ Onyankopɔn teasefoɔ no wɔ mo mu, na pamo na ɔbɛpamo Kanaanfoɔ ne Hetifoɔ ne Hewifoɔ ne Perisifoɔ ne Girgasifoɔ ne Amorifoɔ ne Yebusifoɔ no afiri mo anim.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hwɛ, asase nyinaa wura apam adaka no redi w’anim akɔ Yordan mu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na afei momfa mmarima dummienu mfiri Israel mmusuakuo no mu, abusuakuo biara mu nipa baako.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na sɛ asɔfoɔ a wɔso AWURADE, asase nyinaa wura adaka no anammɔn ka Yordan nsuo no ara pɛ a, Yordan mu nsuo a ɛresiane firi atifi ba no bɛtwa, na abɔ kuo agyina hɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔman no tu firii wɔn ntomadan mu sɛ wɔrekɔtwa Yordan, na asɔfoɔ a wɔso apam adaka no dii ɔman no anim,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na wɔn a wɔso adaka no duruu Yordan ano, na asɔfoɔ a wɔso adaka no nan sii nsuo no mu ara pɛ, (nso na Yordan yiri kata ne nsunoa nyinaa ayutwaberɛ nna nyinaa),",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ɛnna nsuo a ɛfiri atifi ba no gyina bɔɔ kuo baako wɔ akyirikyiri, wɔ Adam, kuro a ɛwɔ Saretan nkyɛn no ho; na nsuo a ɛsiane kɔ mpaperɛ mu po a ɛne Nkyene-po no mu no twa wiee koraa. Na ɔman no twae, Yeriko ntentensoɔ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na asɔfoɔ a wɔso apam adaka no gyinaa asase pɛsɛɛ so Yordan mfimfini pintinn, na Israel nyinaa nam asase pɛsɛɛ so twa de kɔsii sɛ ɔman mu no nyinaa wiee Yordan twa."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɔman mu no nyinaa twaa Yordan wieeɛ no, AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Monyiyi ɔman no mu mmarima dummienu, abusuakuo biara mu onipa baako,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na monhyɛ wɔn sɛ: Montase aboɔ dummienu mfiri Yordan mfimfini ha mfiri deɛ asɔfoɔ no nan gyinaa pintinn hɔ, na momfa ntwa, na monkɔgya no mo asoɛeɛ a mobɛsoɛ hɔ anadwo yi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛnna Yosua frɛɛ mmarima dummienu a ɔyii wɔn firii Israelfoɔ mu no, abusuakuo biara mu onipa baako.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Monsene nni AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn adaka no anim nkɔ Yordan mfimfini, na montase aboɔ mmaako mmaako mmobɔ mo kɔn ho, sɛdeɛ Israelfoɔ mmusuakuo no ano sie, na yei ayɛ mo mu nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Sɛ mo mma bisa mo ɔkyena bi sɛ: Mode aboɔ yi kyerɛ deɛn?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Monka nkyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Ɛkyerɛ sɛ Yordan nsuo no twae, AWURADE apam adaka no anim; ɛtwaa Yordan no, Yordan nsuo no twae; na aboɔ yi nyɛ nkaeɛ mma Israelfoɔ nkɔsi daa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no yɛɛ saa, sɛdeɛ Yosua hyɛeɛ no, na wɔtasee aboɔ dummienu Yordan mu, sɛdeɛ AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Yosua no, sɛ Israelfoɔ mmusuakuo no ano sie, na wɔde twa baa wɔn asoɛeɛ, na wɔgyaa no hɔ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Yosua memaa aboɔ dummienu so sisii Yordan mu, deɛ asɔfoɔ a wɔso apam adaka no nan sisiiɛ hɔ, na ɛwɔ hɔ de bɛsi nnɛ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na asɔfoɔ a wɔso adaka no gyinaa Yordan mu ara de kɔsii sɛ wɔwiee asɛm a AWURADE hyɛɛ Yosua sɛ ɔnka nkyerɛ ɔman no nyinaa sɛ Mose hyɛɛ Yosua no nyinaa. Na ɔman no yɛɛ ntɛm twae.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ ɔman no nyinaa wiee twa no, na AWURADE adaka no nso twaeɛ, na asɔfoɔ no kɔdii ɔman no anim.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Ruben mma ne Gad mma ne Manase abusuakuo fa no miae twa kɔdii Israelfoɔ no anim, sɛdeɛ Mose ka kyerɛɛ wɔn no,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> nnipa bɛyɛ mpemaduanan a wɔasiesie wɔn ho ama ɔko na ɛtwa dii AWURADE anim kɔɔ ɔsa, Yeriko mpaperɛ soɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Da no ara na AWURADE pagyaa Yosua, Israel nyinaa ani so, na wɔsuroo no sɛdeɛ wɔsuroo Mose no, ne nkwa nna nyinaa.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hyɛ asɔfoɔ a wɔso adanseɛ adaka no, na wɔmforo mfiri Yordan mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Yosua hyɛɛ asɔfoɔ no sɛ: Momforo mfiri Yordan mu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na asɔfoɔ a wɔso AWURADE apam adaka no foro firii Yordan mu na asɔfoɔ no anammɔn bɛsii asase pɛsɛɛ soɔ ara pɛ, na Yordan mu nsuo no sane baa n’afa, na ɛbɛkataa ne nsunoa nyinaa sɛdeɛ na ɛteɛ kane no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔman no foro firii Yordan mu bosome a ɛdi kan no da a ɛtɔ so du, na wɔkyeree nsraban Gilgal, Yeriko apueeɛ hyeɛ so.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na aboɔ dummienu a wɔtase firii Yordan mu no, Yosua de sisii Gilgal.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ Israelfoɔ no sɛ: Sɛ ɔkyena bi mo mma bisa wɔn agyanom sɛ: Aboɔ yi kyerɛ deɛn?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Momma mo mma nhunu sɛ asase pɛsɛɛ so na Israel fa de twaa Yordan yi,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> sɛ AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn wee Yordan nsuo no mo anim kɔsii sɛ motwaeɛ, sɛdeɛ AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn yɛɛ Mmɛwa Po no a ɔweeɛ no yɛn anim kɔsii sɛ yɛtwaeɛ no,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> na asase so aman nyinaa ahunu AWURADE nsa sɛ ɛyɛ den, na moasuro AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Amorifoɔ ahene a wɔwɔ Yordan agya atɔeɛ fam no nyinaa ne Kanaan ahemfo a wɔwɔ ɛpo ano no nyinaa tee sɛ AWURADE awe Yordan nsuo Israelfoɔ no anim akɔsi sɛ wɔtwaeɛ no, wɔn akoma tui a na ɔhome bi nni wɔn mu bio Israelfoɔ no anim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Saa berɛ no ara na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Yɛ twerɛboɔ asekan, na sane twitwa Israelfoɔ no twetia a ɛtɔ so mmienu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Yosua yɛɛ twerɛboɔ asekan de twitwaa Israelfoɔ no twetia Aaralot kokoɔ so.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na deɛ enti a Yosua twitwaa wɔn twetia ne sɛ: Ɔman no a wɔfiri Misraim baeɛ no mu mmarima nyinaa, akofoɔ no nyinaa wuwuu kwan mu wɔ serɛ so, wɔfiri Misraim firiiɛ no akyi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Nanso ɔman no a wɔfiri Misraim firiiɛ no akyire wɔwoo wɔn kwan mu wɔ serɛ soɔ no nyinaa deɛ, na wɔntwitwaa wɔn twetia.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Mfirinhyia aduanan na Israelfoɔ no nantee ɛserɛ soɔ kɔsii sɛ akofoɔ a wɔfiri Misraim baeɛ no nyinaa saa korakora, ɛfiri sɛ wɔantie AWURADE nne maa AWURADE kaa wɔn ntam sɛ wɔrenhunu asase a AWURADE kaa wɔn agyanom ntam sɛ ɔde bɛma yɛn no, asase a nufosuo ne ɛwoɔ sene wɔ soɔ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na wɔn mma na ɔmaa wɔsɔre sii wɔn ananmu; wɔn na Yosua twitwaa wɔn twetia, na wɔyɛ momonoto, ɛfiri sɛ wɔantwitwa wɔn twetia ɔkwan no mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na wɔwiee ɔman mu no nyinaa twetiatwa no, wɔtenaa wɔn tenabea hɔ nsraban no mu kɔsii sɛ wɔn ho tɔɔ wɔn.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Ɛnnɛ mamuni Misraim nsopa afiri mo so. Ɛno nti wɔfrɛɛ hɔ Gilgal de bɛsi nnɛ yi ara.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no kyeree nsraban Gilgal, na wɔdii Twam no, bosome no da a ɛtɔ so dunan no anwummerɛ, Yeriko mpaperɛ so.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Twam no akyi, adeɛ kyeeɛ no, da no ara, na wɔdii asase no so aduane, apiti ne nkyeweɛ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na mana no to twae firi da a wɔdii asase no so aduane no, adeɛ kyeeɛ, na Israelfoɔ no annya mana bio, na wɔdii Kanaan asase no so nnɔbaeɛ afe no ara mu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Yosua wɔ Yeriko ho no, ɔmaa n’ani so hwɛe, na hwɛ, ɔbarima bi gyina ne ntentensoɔ kura nkrantɛ a watwe. Na Yosua kɔɔ ne nkyɛn kɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Wowɔ yɛn afa anaa yɛn atamfoɔ afa?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔse: Dabi, na afei na maba sɛ AWURADE dɔm so safohene. Na Yosua de n’anim butuu fam sɔree no, na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na me wura reka akyerɛ n’akoa?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na AWURADE dɔm so safohene no ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Yi wo mpaboa firi wo nan, na deɛ wogyina hɔ yɛ kronkron. Na Yosua yɛɛ saa."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Yeriko deɛ, na wɔato mu na wɔabram ano Israelfoɔ no anim. Obi mfiri adi, na obi mma mu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Hwɛ, mede Yeriko ne ne hene ne akofoɔ no mahyɛ wo nsa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na montwa kuro no ho nhyia; akofoɔ no nyinaa ntwa ho nhyia prɛko. Saa ara na yɛ no nnansia.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na asɔfoɔ baason nkurakura osebɔ ntotorobɛnto nson mfa nni adaka no anim, na ɛda a ɛtɔ so nson no, montwa kuro no ho nhyia mprɛnson, na asɔfoɔ no nhyɛne ntotorobɛnto no.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na sɛ wɔhyɛne osebɔ abɛn no na mote totorobɛnto no nne a, ɔman no nyinaa nhuro mmɔ ose kɛseɛ, na kuro no ho fasuo no bɛhwe fam tim, na ɔman no mforo nkɔ wɔn anim tee.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Nun ba Yosua frɛfrɛɛ asɔfoɔ no, na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Monsoa apam adaka no, na asɔfoɔ baason nkurakura osebɔ ntotorobɛnto nni AWURADE adaka no anim.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na wɔka kyerɛɛ ɔman no sɛ: Monsene nkɔtwa kuro no ho nhyia, na wɔn a wɔamia no nsene nni AWURADE adaka no anim.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ ɔman no no, asɔfoɔ baason a wɔkurakura osebɔ ntotorobɛnto no sene dii AWURADE anim na wɔhyɛnee ntotorobɛnto no, na AWURADE apam adaka no dii wɔn akyi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wɔn a wɔamia no dii asɔfoɔ a wɔhyɛne ntotorobɛnto no anim, na kyidɔm no dii adaka no akyi; wɔnam na wɔrehyɛne ntotorobɛnto no ara.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɔman no deɛ, Yosua hyɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Mommmɔ ose, na mommma wɔnnte mo nne, na asɛm biara mmfiri mo anomu de kɔsi da a mɛse mo sɛ mommɔ ose no ansa na moabɔ ose.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na AWURADE adaka no twaa kuro no ho hyiaa prɛko, na wɔbaa nsraban mu bɛdaa hɔ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Yosua sɔree anɔpahema, na asɔfoɔ no soaa AWURADE adaka no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na asɔfoɔ baason no kurakura osebɔ ntotorobɛnto nson no de di AWURADE adaka no anim, wɔnam na wɔrehyɛne ntotorobɛnto no ara, na wɔn a wɔamia no dii wɔn anim, na kyidɔm no dii AWURADE adaka no akyi, wɔnam na wɔrehyɛne ntotorobɛnto no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na da a ɛtɔ so mmienu no, wɔtwaa kuro no ho hyiaa prɛko, na wɔsane baa nsraban no mu. Wɔyɛɛ saa nnansia.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na da a ɛtɔ so nson no, adeɛ rekye pɛ, na wɔtuaa nhema sɔree ntɛm, na wɔtwaa kuro no ho hyiaa saa ara mprɛnson; da no nko ara na wɔtwaa kuro no ho hyiaa mprɛnson.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ deɛ ɛtɔ so nson no soɔ a asɔfoɔ no rehyɛne ntotorobɛnto no no, Yosua ka kyerɛɛ ɔman no sɛ: Mommɔ ose, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE de kuro no ama mo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na kuro no nyɛ ahyiradeɛ, ɛno ne emu ade nyinaa mma AWURADE; odwamamfoɔ Rahab nko ara na ɔnnya nkwa, ɔno ne wɔn a wɔwɔ ne nkyɛn ne ne fie nyinaa, ɛfiri sɛ ɔno na ɔde abɔfoɔ a yɛsomaa wɔn no huntaeɛ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Mo ho yie ara na monhwɛ ahyiradeɛ no ho, na moanhyira so na moamfa ahyiradeɛ no bi, na moamfa Israel nsraban no anyɛ ahyiradeɛ amma amaneɛ amma so.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na dwetɛ ne sika, ne kɔbere mfrafraeɛ ne dadeɛ nnoɔma nyinaa nyɛ kronkron mma AWURADE, na wɔmfa mmra AWURADE adekorabea.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ɛnna ɔman no bɔɔ ose na wɔhyɛnee ntotorobɛnto no. Na ɛbaa sɛ ɔman no tee ntotorobɛnto no nne no, ɔman no huro bɔɔ ose kɛseɛ, na ɔfasuo no hwee fam tim, na ɔman no foro kɔɔ kuro no mu, wɔn nyinaa kɔɔ wɔn anim tee, na wɔfaa kuro no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔde nkrantɛ ano sɛee deɛ ɛwɔ kuro no mu nyinaa pasapasa, mmarima ne mmaa, mmɔfra ne mpanin, anantwie ne nnwan ne mfunumu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na mmarima baanu a wɔkɔsraa asase no deɛ, Yosua ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Monkɔ ɔbaa dwamamfoɔ no fie nkɔfa ɔbaa no ne deɛ ɔwɔ nyinaa mfiri hɔ, sɛdeɛ mokaa no ntam no.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na mmeranteɛ akwansrafoɔ no kɔe, na wɔde Rahab ne n’agya ne ne na ne ne nuanom ne deɛ ɔwɔ nyinaa firi bae, na wɔde n’abusua nyinaa firii adi bɛgyaa wɔn Israel nsraban no akyi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na kuro no deɛ, wɔde ogya hyee ɛne deɛ ɛwɔ mu nyinaa. Emu dwetɛ ne sika, ne kɔbere mfrafraeɛ ne dadeɛ nnoɔma nko na wɔde bɛguu AWURADE fie adekorabea no mu.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na odwamamfoɔ Rahab ne n’agya fie ne deɛ ɔwɔ nyinaa deɛ, Yosua gyee wɔn nkwa, na ɔtenaa Israel mu de bɛsi nnɛ, ɛfiri sɛ ɔde abɔfoɔ a Yosua soma maa wɔkɔsraa Yeriko no huntae.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Yosua kaa ntam saa berɛ no sɛ: Nnome nka onipa a ɔbɛsɔre abɛkyekyere Yeriko kuro yi, AWURADE anim: Ɔde n’abakan na ɛbɛhyɛ aseɛ, na ɔde ne ba akumaa na ɛbɛsisi ano apono.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na AWURADE dii Yosua akyi, na wɔtee ne nka asase no nyinaa so."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no too ahyiradeɛ no ho mmara, na Sera ba Sabdi ba Karmi ba Akan a ɔfiri Yuda abusuakuo mu no faa ahyiradeɛ no bi, na AWURADE bo fuu Israelfoɔ no.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Yosua somaa mmarima bi firi Yeriko kɔɔ Ai a ɛwɔ Bet-awen ho, Betel apueeɛ, na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Monkɔ nkɔsra asase no. Na mmarima no kɔ kɔsraa Ai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na wɔsane baa Yosua nkyɛn bɛka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Mma ɔman no nyinaa mmforo nnkɔ; na mmarima bɛyɛ mpennu anaa mpensa nkɔbɔ Ai, nha ɔman no nyinaa mma wɔnnkɔ hɔ, na wɔsua.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔman no mu bɛyɛ mpensa foro kɔɔ hɔ, nanso wɔdwane firii Ai mmarima no anim.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Ai mmarima no kunkumm wɔn mu nnipa bɛyɛ aduasa nsia, na wɔtaa wɔn Ai kuro pono no akyi de kɔɔ Sebarim, na wɔbobɔɔ wɔn asianee no mu. Na ɔman no akoma tui, na ɛyɛɛ sɛ nsuo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Yosua sunsuanee ne ntadeɛ mu, na ɔde n’anim butuu fam, AWURADE adaka no anim de kɔsii anwummerɛ, ɔno ne Israel mpanimfoɔ, na wɔde dɔteɛ guguu wɔn atifi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Yosua kaa sɛ: AWURADE Nyankopɔn, adɛn nti na wode ɔman yi twaa Yordan sɛ wode yɛn rebɛhyɛ Amorifoɔ nsa na wɔasɛe yɛn? Yɛnim a, anka yɛpene tenaa Yordan agya hɔ ara.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Wo kyɛw nie, AWURADE, sɛ Israel adane wɔn akyi akyerɛ wɔn atamfoɔ yi, ɛdeɛn na menka?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Kanaanfoɔ ne asase yi sofoɔ nyinaa bɛte, na wɔabɛtwa yɛn ho ahyia, na wɔatwa yɛn din afiri asase so: Na ɛdeɛn na wobɛyɛ ama wo din kɛseɛ no?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Sɔre ɛ, adɛn nti na wode w’anim abutu fam seyie?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Israel ayɛ bɔne, wɔato m’apam a mehyɛɛ wɔn ho mmara no nso, na wɔafa ahyiradeɛ no bi nso, na wɔabɔ korɔno nso, na wɔasi so nso, na wɔde asie wɔn adeɛ mu nso.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no rentumi nnyina wɔn atamfoɔ anim, wɔn akyiri na wɔbɛdane akyerɛ wɔn atamfoɔ, ɛfiri sɛ wɔayɛ ahyiradeɛ. Merenkɔ so menni mo akyi, gye sɛ moyi ahyiradeɛ no hɔ firi mo mu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Sɔre te ɔman no ho na ka sɛ: Monyɛ mo ho kronkron nsie ɔkyena; na sɛ AWURADE, Israel Nyankopɔn no seɛ nie: Ahyiradeɛ wɔ wo mu, Israel! Worentumi nnyina w’atamfo anim kɔsi sɛ mobɛyi ahyiradeɛ no afiri mo mu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Enti anɔpa, wɔmfa mo mpinkyɛ mmusuakuo mmusuakuo. Na abusuakuo a AWURADE bɛkyerɛ no ntwe mpini mmusua mmusua, na abusua a AWURADE bɛkyerɛ no ntwe mpini afie, na efie a AWURADE bɛkyerɛ no mu mmarima ntwe mpini mmaako mmaako.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na deɛ wɔbɛkye no ahyiradeɛ no ho no, wɔmfa ogya nhye no ne deɛ ɔwɔ nyinaa, sɛ wato AWURADE ntam, na wayɛ nkwaseadeɛ Israel mu.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛnna Yosua sɔree anɔpahema, na ɔde Israel pinkyɛe abusuakuo abusuakuo. Na wɔkyeree Yuda abusuakuo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔde Yuda mmusua pinkyɛe, na wɔkyeree Serafoɔ abusua. Na ɔde Serafoɔ abusua mu mmarima pinkyɛe mmaako mmaako, na wɔkyeree Sabdi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔde ne fie mmarima pinkyɛe mmaako mmaako, na wɔkyeree Sera ba Sabdi ba Karmi ba Akan a ɔfiri Yuda abusuakuo mu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ Akan sɛ: Me ba, fa animuonyam ma AWURADE, Israel Nyankopɔn, na di no ni, na ka kyerɛ me ɛ: Ɛdeɛn na woyɛeɛ? Nsi me so.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Akan buaa Yosua sɛ: Nokorɛ, me na mayɛ AWURADE, Israel Nyankopɔn no, bɔne, na sɛɛ ne sɛɛ na meyɛeɛ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Mehunuu asadeɛ no mu Sinear ngusoɔ fɛfɛ bi ne dwetɛ nnwetɛbena ahanu ne sika dame baako a ano si nnwetɛbena aduonum, na m’ani beree, na mefae; na hwɛ, ɛhyɛ fam me ntomadan mu, na dwetɛ no wɔ aseɛ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛnna Yosua somaa abɔfoɔ, na wɔde mmirika kɔɔ ntomadan no mu, na hwɛ, na ɛhyɛ ne ntomadan no mu, na dwetɛ no hyɛ aseɛ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔyi firii ntomadan no mu de brɛɛ Yosua ne Israelfoɔ no nyinaa, na wɔde bɛguu AWURADE anim.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ɛnna Yosua faa Sera ba Akan, ne dwetɛ ne ngusoɔ ne sika dame no, ne ne mmammarima ne ne mmammaa, ne n’anantwie ne ne mfunumu ne ne nnwan, ne ne ntomadan ne deɛ ɔwɔ nyinaa, na Israel nyinaa ka ne ho, na wɔde wɔn foro kɔɔ Akor bonhwa mu.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Yosua kaa sɛ: Adɛn na woaha yɛn saa yi? AWURADE bɛha wo nnɛ da yi. Na Israel nyinaa sii no aboɔ, na wɔde ogya hyee wɔn, na wɔde aboɔ guu wɔn so.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na wɔhɔree ne so abosie kɛseɛ a ɛwɔ hɔ de bɛsi nnɛ yi. Na AWURADE dane firii n’abufuhyeɛ no ho. Ɛno nti wɔfrɛ hɔ sɛ Akor bonhwa de bɛsi nnɛ yi."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Nsuro, na mma w’akoma nntu. Fa akofoɔ dɔm no nyinaa ka wo ho, na sɔre foro kɔ Ai: Hwɛ, mede Ai hene ne ne man ne ne kuro ne n’asase mahyɛ wo nsa.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na yɛ Ai ne ne hene sɛdeɛ woyɛɛ Yeriko ne ne hene no: Emu asadeɛ ne mmoa nko na momfom mfa. Fa atɛfoɔ ma wɔnkɔtɛ kuro no akyiri mma wo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Yosua sɔree, ɔno ne akofoɔ dɔm no nyinaa sɛ wɔreforo akɔ Ai. Na Yosua yiyii mmarima akofoɔ mpem aduasa, na ɔgyaa wɔn kwan anadwo no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔhyɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Monhwɛ, monkɔtɛ kuro no, kuro no akyiri nohoa; mommma mo ne kuro no ntam nnware bebree, na mo nyinaa nnyina ahoboa mu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na me deɛ, me ne nnipa a wɔka me ho no nyinaa bɛtwe apini kuro no; na sɛ wɔfiri adi bɛhyia yɛn sɛ akane no a, yɛbɛdwane afiri wɔn anim;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na wɔbɛfiri adi abɛdi yɛn akyi akɔsi sɛ yɛbɛtwe wɔn afiri kuro no mu; na wɔbɛka sɛ: Wɔredwane afiri yɛn anim sɛ akane no; enti yɛbɛdwane afiri wɔn anim.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na mo deɛ, monsɔre mfiri ɔtɛ no mu, na momfa kuro no, na AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn de bɛhyɛ mo nsa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na sɛ monya fa kuro no a, monto kuro no mu gya; monyɛ no sɛdeɛ AWURADE ahyɛ no; monhwɛ, hyɛ na mahyɛ mo no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɛnna Yosua gyaa wɔn kwan, na wɔsii mu kɔe kɔtɛe. Na wɔtenaa Betel ne Ai ntam, Ai atɔeɛ fam; na Yosua daa ɔman no mu anadwo no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Yosua sɔree anɔpahema siesiee ɔman no, na ɔno ne Israel mpanimfoɔ foro dii ɔman no anim kɔɔ Ai.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na akofoɔ dɔm a wɔka ne ho nyinaa foro kɔe, na wɔtwe pinii, na wɔduruu kuro no ntentensoɔ, na wɔbɔɔ nsraban Ai atifi fam, na bonhwa wɔ wɔn ne Ai ntam.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔde nnipa bɛyɛ mpemnum kɔtetɛɛ Betel ne Ai ntam, kuro no atɔeɛ fam.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔde dɔm no sisii, ɛdɔm a wɔwɔ kuro no atifi fam ne akyire atɛfoɔ no a ɛwɔ kuro no atɔeɛ fam no nyinaa; na Yosua kɔɔ bonhwa no mu anadwo no ara.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Ai hene hunuiɛ no, ɔne ne man nyinaa, kuro no mu mmarima no, yɛɛ ntɛm tuaa ahema kɔɔ deɛ wɔahyɛ hɔ, mpaperɛ no anim, sɛ wɔrebɛhyia Israel ne wɔn ako; nso na ɔnnim sɛ wɔretɛ no kuro no akyi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Yosua ne Israel nyinaa maa wɔpamoo wɔn wɔn anim, na wɔdwane faa ɛserɛ so kwan so.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛnna wɔteaa mu frɛɛ ɔman a wɔwɔ kuro no mu nyinaa sɛ wɔmmɛti wɔn; na wɔtii Yosua, na wɔtwee wɔn firii kuro no mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔbarima biara anka Ai ne Betel a wamfiri adi ankɔdi Israel akyire; na wɔgyaa kuro no hɔ maa ano daa hɔ kɔdii Israel akyi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛnna AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Tene pea a ɛwɔ wo nsam no kyerɛ Ai, na mede bɛhyɛ wo nsa. Na Yosua tenee ne pea a ɛwɔ ne nsam no kyerɛɛ kuro no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ɛnna atɛfoɔ no sɔree ntɛm firii wɔn afa hɔ, na ɔtenee ne nsa no, wɔtutuu mmirika kɔhyɛnee kuro no mu na wɔfae, na wɔyɛɛ ntɛm de ogya too kuro no mu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Ai mmarima no danedanee wɔn ani hwɛɛ wɔn akyiri no, na hwɛ, na kuro no mu wisie retu kɔ soro, na wɔnnya kwan nnwane nkɔ ha anaa ha. Na nnipa a wɔdwane kɔɔ ɛserɛ soɔ no danedanee wɔn ho tiaa atifoɔ no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Yosua ne Israel nyinaa hunuu sɛ atɛfoɔ no afa kuro no, na kuro no mu wisie retu kɔ soro no, wɔsanee wɔn akyi bɛkunkumm Ai mmarima no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na yeinom nso firii adi firii kuro no mu bɛhyiaa wɔn, na wɔtɔɔ Israel ntam, yeinom wɔ ha, na yeinom nso wɔ ha; na wɔkunkumm wɔn ara kɔsii sɛ wɔn mu anikanfoɔ anaa odwanefoɔ biara anka.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Ai hene no, wɔkyeree no animono, na wɔde no brɛɛ Yosua.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Israel wiee Aifoɔ nyinaa kum wɔ ɛserɛ so petee mu, faako a wɔbɛtii wɔn no, na wɔn nyinaa totɔɔ nkrantɛ ano kɔsii sɛ wɔsaeɛ no, Israel nyinaa sane kɔɔ Ai de nkrantɛ ano kunkumm wɔn.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na nnipa a wɔtotɔɔ da no nyinaa, mmarima ne mmaa yɛ mpem dummienu, Aifoɔ nyinaa.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Yosua antwe ne nsa a ɔde tenee ne pea no de kɔsii sɛ wɔsɛee Aifoɔ nyinaa pasapasa.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kuro no mu mmoa ne asadeɛ nko na Israel fom faeɛ, sɛ AWURADE asɛm a ɔde hyɛɛ Yosua no teɛ no.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na Yosua hyee Ai na ɔyɛɛ no daa amamfo sie de bɛsi nnɛ yi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na Ai hene no deɛ, ɔsɛnee no dua so kɔsii anwummerɛ; na owia kɔtɔeɛ no, Yosua hyɛɛ sɛ wɔnkɔyi ne funu no mfiri dua no so, na wɔde no too kuro no pono ano, na wɔhɔree ne so aboɔsie kɛseɛ a ɛwɔ hɔ de bɛsi nnɛ yi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ɛnna Yosua kɔsii afɔrebukyia maa AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn Ebal bepɔ soɔ,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> sɛdeɛ AWURADE akoa Mose hyɛɛ Israelfoɔ no sɛdeɛ wɔatwerɛ no Mose mmara nwoma no mu no, afɔrebukyia a wɔde aboɔ amuamu a obi mmaa dadeɛ so wɔ so pɛn asie; na wɔbɔɔ so ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ maa AWURADE, na wɔkunkumm asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na aboɔ no so hɔ na ɔtwerɛɛ Mose mmara ntimu a ɔtwerɛɛ no Israelfoɔ anim no.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na Israel nyinaa ne wɔn mpanimfoɔ ne ahwɛfoɔ ne wɔn atemmufoɔ gyinaa adaka no ho ha ne ha, asɔfoɔ Lewifoɔ a wɔso AWURADE apam adaka no anim, ɔhɔhoɔ ne ɔman ba nyinaa. Wɔn mu fa wɔ Gerisim bepɔ ntentensoɔ, na ɔfa nso wɔ Ebal bepɔ ntentensoɔ, sɛdeɛ AWURADE akoa Mose hyɛɛ sɛ wɔnhyira ɔman Israel kane no.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na ɛno akyiri no, ɔkenkanee mmara mu nsɛm no nyinaa, nhyira no ne nnome no, sɛdeɛ wɔatwerɛ no nwoma no mu nyinaa.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Deɛ Mose hyɛeɛ no nyinaa mu asɛm biara nni hɔ a Yosua ankenkan no Israel dwabɔ nyinaa ne mmaa ne mmɔfra ne ɔhɔhoɔ a ɔnam wɔn mu no anim."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ahemfo a wɔwɔ Yordan agya ha fam mmepɔ so nyinaa ne Sefela mpaperɛ so ne ɛpo kɛseɛ no ano nyinaa de kɔ Lebanon ntentensoɔ, Hetifoɔ ne Amorifoɔ, Kanaanfoɔ ne Perisifoɔ ne Hewifoɔ ne Yebusifoɔ no teeɛ no,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> wɔbɛhyia boaa wɔn ano yɛɛ nokorɔ sɛ wɔne Yosua ne Israel rebɛko.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Gibeonfoɔ tee deɛ Yosua yɛɛ Yeriko ne Ai no,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> wɔn deɛ, wɔdii no nyansam na wɔkɔpɛɛ akwansoduane, na wɔfaa mmɔtɔ adada de soasoaa wɔn mfunumu ne nsa nkotokuo adada a asunsuane na wɔapempam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na wɔde mpaboa adada a wɔasesa kyekyeree wɔn nan, na wɔhyehyɛɛ ntadeɛ agoago, na wɔn kwan so paanoo nyinaa akyenkyen na abobɔ atuo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wɔsii mu baa Yosua nkyɛn nsraban mu wɔ Gilgal bɛka kyerɛɛ no ne Israel mmarima no sɛ: Akyirikyiri asase bi so na yɛfiri baeɛ, na afei mo ne yɛn nyɛ apam.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Israel mmarima no ka kyerɛɛ Hewifoɔ no sɛ: Ebia yɛn mu na woteɛ; na ɛbɛyɛ dɛn na yɛne wo bɛyɛ apam?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛnna wɔka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Wo nkoa ne yɛn. Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Hwannom ne mo, na ɛhe na mofire?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wɔse: AWURADE wo Nyankopɔn no din nti na wo nkoa firi akyirikyiri asase bi so aba, ɛfiri sɛ yɛate ne nka ne deɛ ɔyɛɛ no Misraim nyinaa",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ne deɛ ɔyɛɛ Amorifoɔ ahemfo baanu a wɔwɔ Yordan agya no, Hesbon hene Sihon ne Basan hene Og a ɔtenaa Astarot no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na yɛn mpanimfoɔ ne yɛn asase no sofoɔ nyinaa ka kyerɛɛ yɛn sɛ: Momfa akwansoduane na monkɔ nkɔhyia wɔn, na monka nkyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Mo nkoa ne yɛn, na afei mo ne yɛn nyɛ apam.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Yɛn paanoo nie, ɛda a yɛresim aba mo nkyɛn no, yɛfaa no hyehyeɛ de firii yɛn afie mu, sɛ yɛrebɛdi no ɔkwan so; na afei, monhwɛ, akyenkyen na abobɔ atuo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na nsa nkotokuo yi a yɛhyehyɛɛ no amaama na ɛyɛ foforɔ no, hwɛ, asunsuane, na ɔkwan no ware a ɛware pii nti yɛn ntadeɛ ne yɛn mpaboa yi asusu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na mmarima no faa wɔn akwansoduane no bi, na AWURADE anomu asɛm deɛ, wɔammisa.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Yosua ne wɔn dii no asomdwoeɛ mu, na ɔne wɔn yɛɛ apam sɛ wɔbɛma wɔatena ase; na asafo no mu mmapɔmma kekaa wɔn ntam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na wɔne wɔn yɛɛ apam no akyiri nnansa no, wɔtee sɛ wɔbɛn wɔn na wɔte wɔn mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Israelfoɔ tui, na wɔkɔtoo wɔn nkuro da a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa no; na wɔn nkuro ne Gibeon ne Kefira ne Beerot ne Kiriat-yearim.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no anku wɔn, ɛfiri sɛ asafo no mu mmapɔmma akeka wɔn AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn no ntam. Na asafo no nyinaa nwiinwii tiaa mmapɔmma no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na mmapɔmma no nyinaa ka kyerɛɛ asafo no nyinaa sɛ: Yɛaka wɔn AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn ntam, enti ɛnsɛ sɛ yɛka wɔn.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Yei na yɛbɛyɛ wɔn, na yɛama wɔatena ase, na ntam a yɛkaa wɔn no nti, abufuo amma yɛn so.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na mmapɔmma no ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Wɔntena ase, na wɔnyɛ nnuatwafoɔ ne nsusafoɔ mma asafo no nyinaa, sɛdeɛ mmapɔmma no ka kyerɛɛ wɔn no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Yosua frɛɛ wɔn bae, na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Adɛn nti na modaadaa yɛn kaa sɛ: Yɛne mo ntam ware pa ara, nanso mote yɛn mu yi?",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Enti afei wɔadome mo, na mo mu na nkoa ne nnuatwafoɔ ne nsusafoɔ a wɔbɛyɛ adwuma ama ne Nyankopɔn fie no bɛfire daa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na wɔbuaa Yosua sɛ: Ampa ara, wɔka kyerɛɛ wo nkoa sɛ AWURADE wo Nyankopɔn ahyɛ n’akoa Mose sɛ ɔmfa asase no nyinaa mma mo na ɔnsɛe asase no sofoɔ nyinaa mfiri mo anim no, na mo nti yɛsuroo yɛn nkwa ho papaapa, enti na yɛdii saa asɛm yi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na afei, yɛn nie, yɛwɔ wo nsam, deɛ ɛyɛ na ɛtene w’ani soɔ a wobɛyɛ yɛn no, yɛ!",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ wɔn saa, na ɔyii wɔn firii Israelfoɔ nsam, na wɔanku wɔn.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na da no ara Yosua de wɔn yɛɛ nnuatwafoɔ ne nsusafoɔ maa asafo no ne AWURADE afɔrebukyia no sɛ ɛntoa so mmɛsi nnɛ yi faako a ɔbɛyie."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Yerusalem hene Adoni-sedek tee sɛ Yosua afa Ai na wasɛe no pasapasa, ne sɛdeɛ ɔyɛɛ Yeriko ne ne hene no, saa ara na wayɛ Ai ne ne hene nso,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ne sɛ Gibeonfoɔ ne Israel adi asomdwoeɛsɛm na wɔaba wɔn mu no, wɔsuroo papaapa, ɛfiri sɛ Gibeon yɛ kuro kɛseɛ te sɛ ahennie nkuro no bi, na ɛso sene Ai, na emu mmarima nyinaa yɛ nnɔmmarima.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Yerusalemhene Adoni-sedek soma maa wɔkɔɔ Hebronhene Hoham ne Yarmuthene Piram ne Lakishene Yafia ne Eglonhene Debir nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Mommra me nkyɛn mmɛboa me, na yɛnkunkum Gibeon, ɛfiri sɛ wɔne Yosua ne Israelfoɔ no akɔdi asomdwoeɛsɛm.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Amorifoɔ ahemfo baanum boaboaa wɔn ano bae, Yerusalem hene, Hebron hene, Yarmut hene, Lakis hene, Eglon hene, wɔne wɔn dɔm nyinaa, na wɔbɛkyeree Gibeon so nsraban sɛ wɔne wɔn rebɛko.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛnna Gibeonfoɔ no soma maa wɔbaa Yosua nkyɛn Gilgal nsraban no mu sɛ: Nyi wo nsa mfiri wo nkoa so, bra yɛn nkyɛn bɛgye yɛn nkwa na di boa yɛn, na Amorifoɔ a wɔte mmepɔ soɔ ahemfo nyinaa abɛhyia atia yɛn.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛnna Yosua firii Gilgal foro kɔeɛ, ɔno ne akofoɔ no nyinaa ne nnɔmmarima nyinaa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Nsuro wɔn, na wo nsa na mede wɔn mahyɛ, wɔn mu biara rennyina w’anim.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Yosua baa wɔn so mpofirim, ɔde anadwo mu no nyinaa na ɛforo firii Gilgal baeɛ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na AWURADE tanee wɔn ani Israel anim, na wɔde okunkɛseɛ kunkumm wɔn wɔ Gibeon, na wɔtii wɔn Bet-horon aforoeɛ kwan no so, na wɔkunkumm wɔn de kɔsii Aseka ne Makeda.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔredwane afiri Israel anim na wɔkɔduruu Bet-horon asianee mu no, AWURADE totoo aboɔ akɛseɛ firi soro guguu wɔn so de kɔduruu Aseka maa wɔwuwui, wɔn a asukɔtweaa no kunkumm wɔn no dɔɔso sene wɔn a Israelfoɔ no kunkumm wɔn nkrantɛ ano no.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛno mu na Yosua kasa kyerɛɛ AWURADE, da a AWURADE de Amorifoɔ maa Israel anim no, na ɔkaa no Israel anim sɛ: Owia, twɛn wɔ Gibeon, ne ɔsrane, wɔ Ayalon bonhwa mu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na owia twɛnee, na ɔsrane gyinae de kɔsii sɛ ɛdɔm no tɔɔ wɔn atamfoɔ so were. Wɔntwerɛɛ yei Teefoɔ Nwoma no mu? Na owia gyinaa ɔsoro mfimfini, na ampɛ ntɛm ankɔtɔ bɛyɛ da mu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɛda bi mmae sɛ ɛno, anim anaa akyire a AWURADE atie onipa nne, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE ko maa Israel.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Yosua sane ne Israel nyinaa baa Gilgal nsraban no mu.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ahemfo baanum yi dwane kɔhuntaa Makeda ɔbodan no mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na wɔbɛka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Yɛahunu ahemfo baanum no sɛ wɔahunta Makeda ɔbodan no mu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Yosua kaa sɛ: Monkɔmuni aboɔ akɛseɛ nhini ɔbodan no ano, na momfa mmarima nnyina ho mma wɔnwɛn wɔn.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na mo deɛ, monnnyina hɔ, monti mo atamfoɔ no, na monkum wɔn kyidɔm no; mommma wɔnnnuru wɔn nkuro mu, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn de wɔn ahyɛ mo nsa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Yosua ne Israelfoɔ no de okunkɛseɛ pa kunkum wɔn wieeɛ maa wɔsaeɛ no, na nnipa a wɔfirii mu no dwanedwane kɔhyɛnehyɛnee nkuro a wɔatoto ho afasuo mu,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na ɔman no nyinaa sane baa nsraban no mu Yosua nkyɛn wɔ Makeda dwoodwoo. Obiara antwe ne tɛkyerɛma antia Israelfoɔ no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Yosua kaa sɛ: Mommue ɔbodan no ano, na monyi ahemfo baanum no mfiri ɔbodan no mu mmrɛ me.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔyɛɛ saa, na wɔyiyii ahemfo baanum no firii ɔbodan no mu brɛɛ no: Yerusalem hene, Hebron hene, Yarmut hene, Lakis hene, Eglon hene.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na wɔde ahemfo yi firi brɛɛ Yosua no, Yosua frɛɛ Israel mmarima nyinaa bae, na ɔsee mmarima akofoɔ a wɔne no kɔeɛ no asafohene no sɛ: Montwe mpini mfa mo nan mmɛsisi ahemfo yi kɔn so. Na wɔtwe pinii de wɔn nan bɛsisii wɔn kɔn so.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Monnsuro, na mo akoma nntu, mo ho nyɛ den na monyɛ nnam. Na saa ara na AWURADE bɛyɛ mo atamfoɔ a mo ne wɔn ko no nyinaa.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ɛno akyiri no, Yosua bobɔɔ wɔn kunkumm wɔn, na ɔde wɔn sensɛnee nnua nnum so, na wɔsensɛnee nnua no so kɔsii anwummerɛ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na owia rekɔtɔ no, Yosua hyɛe maa wɔyiyii wɔn firii nnua no so, na wɔkɔtoo wɔn guu ɔbodan a wɔkɔhuntaa mu no mu, na wɔde aboɔ akɛseɛ guu ɔbodan no ano a ɛwɔ hɔ de bɛsi nnɛ yi ara.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na Yosua faa Makeda da no ara, na ɔde nkrantɛ ano kunkumm wɔn, ne emu hene nso; na ɔsɛee akra a wɔwɔ mu nyinaa pasapasa, wamma obiara anka, na ɔyɛɛ Makeda hene sɛdeɛ ɔyɛɛ Yeriko hene no.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ɛnna Yosua ne Israel a wɔka ne ho nyinaa twaa mu firii Makeda kɔɔ Libna, na ɔne Libna kɔkoeɛ.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na AWURADE de ɛno nso hyɛɛ Israel nsa ne emu hene, na ɔde nkrantɛ ano kumm akra a wɔwɔ mu no nyinaa, wamma obiara anka wɔ mu, na ɔyɛɛ ne hene no sɛdeɛ ɔyɛɛ Yeriko hene no.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na Yosua ne Israel a wɔka ne ho nyinaa twaa mu firii Libna kɔɔ Lakis, na ɔkyeree so nsraban, na ɔne wɔn koe.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na AWURADE de Lakis hyɛɛ Israel nsa, na wɔfae, da a ɛtɔ so mmienu no, na ɔde nkrantɛ ano kunkumm wɔn ne akra a wɔwɔ mu nyinaa, sɛdeɛ ɔyɛɛ Libna no ara.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ɛno mu no Geser hene Horam foro ba bɛboaa Lakis. Na Yosua kumm no ne ne man nyinaa de kɔsii sɛ wamma no anka no obiara.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ɛnna Yosua ne Israel a wɔka ne ho nyinaa twaa mu firii Lakis kɔɔ Eglon, na wɔkyeree so nsraban, na wɔne wɔn koe.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na wɔfae, da no ara, na wɔde nkrantɛ ano kunkumm wɔn ne nnipa a ɛwɔ mu nyinaa; da no ara na ɔsɛee wɔn pasapasa sɛdeɛ ɔyɛɛ Lakis no ara.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ɛnna Yosua ne Israel a wɔka ne ho nyinaa foro firii Eglon kɔɔ Hebron, na ɔne wɔn koe.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na wɔfae de nkrantɛ ano kunkumm wɔn ne emu hene ne wɔn nkuro no nyinaa ne akra a ɛwɔ mu nyinaa. Wamma obiara anka, sɛdeɛ ɔyɛɛ Eglon no ara, na ɔsɛee ɛno ne akra a ɛwɔ mu nyinaa pasapasa.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ɛnna Yosua ne Israel a wɔka ne ho nyinaa sane baa Debir ne no bɛkoeɛ.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na ɔfae, ne ne hene ne ne nkuro nyinaa, na wɔde nkrantɛ ano kunkumm wɔn, na wɔsɛee akra a ɛwɔ mu nyinaa pasapasa, wamma obiara anka, sɛdeɛ ɔyɛɛ Hebron ne Libna ne ne hene no, saa na ɔyɛɛ Debir ne ne hene.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na Yosua sɛee asase no nyinaa: Mmepɔ no ne Negeb ne ɛpo ho mpaperɛ so ne mmepɔ ase ne wɔn ahemfo nyinaa; wannya odwanefoɔ biara, na adeɛ biara a ɛhome no, ɔsɛee no pasapasa, sɛdeɛ AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn hyɛeɛ no.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Na Yosua kunkumm wɔn firii Kades-barnea kɔduruu Gasa ne Gosen asase no nyinaa kɔduruu Gibeon.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na ahemfo yi nyinaa ne wɔn asase no Yosua faa no prɛko, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn ko maa Israel.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Na Yosua ne Israel a wɔka ne ho no nyinaa sane baa Gilgal nsraban no mu."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Hasorhene Yabin teeɛ no, ɔsoma maa wɔkɔɔ Madonhene Yobab ne Simronhene ne Aksafhene nkyɛn",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ne ahemfo a wɔwɔ atifi fam mmepɔ soɔ ne Kinerot anafoɔ fam mpaperɛ so ne Dor nkokoɔ so, atɔeɛ po fam",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kanafoɔ a wɔwɔ apueeɛ ne atɔeɛ ne Amorifoɔ ne Hetifoɔ ne Perisifoɔ ne mmepɔ so Yebusifoɔ ne Hewifoɔ a wɔwɔ Hermon bepɔ ase Mispa asase soɔ no nkyɛn.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔn ne wɔn dɔm a ɛka wɔn ho no nyinaa firi bae, nnipa pepeankoma a wɔn dodoɔ te sɛ mpoano anwea ne apɔnkɔ ne nteaseɛnam pii pa ara.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ahemfo yi nyinaa bɛhyiae, na wɔba bɛkyekyeree nsraban faako, Merom asuo ho sɛ wɔne Israel rebɛko.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Nsuro wɔn na ɔkyena sɛsɛɛ berɛ yi mu, me na mɛma woaku wɔn nyinaa Israel anim. Wɔn apɔnkɔ no, twitwa wɔn nantin, na wɔn nteaseɛnam no, fa ogya hye.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛnna Yosua ne akofoɔ dɔm a wɔka ne ho no nyinaa baa wɔn soɔ mpofirim, Merom asuo no ano bɛtuaa wɔn.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na AWURADE de wɔn hyɛɛ Israel nsa na wɔkunkumm wɔn na wɔtaa wɔn de kɔduruu Sidon kɛseɛ ne Misrefot-maim ho ne Mispa bonhwa no mu apueeɛ fam, na wɔkunkum wɔn de kɔsii sɛ wɔannya wɔn odwanefoɔ biara.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Yosua yɛɛ wɔn sɛdeɛ AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ no no, wɔn apɔnkɔ no, ɔtwitwaa wɔn nantin, na wɔn nteaseɛnam no, ɔde ogya hyee.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Yosua sanee berɛ no ara mu bɛfaa Hasor, na ɔde nkrantɛ kumm ne hene. Na akane no na Hasor ne saa ahennie yi nyinaa ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔde nkrantɛ ano kunkumm akra a ɛwɔ mu nyinaa sɛee wɔn pasapasa, wɔannya biribiara a ɛhome, na ɔde ogya hyee Hasor.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ahemfo yi nkuro nyinaa ne emu ahemfo nyinaa, Yosua fae, na ɔde nkrantɛ ano kunkumm wɔn sɛee wɔn pasapasa, sɛdeɛ AWURADE akoa Mose hyɛeɛ no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nanso nkuro a ɛda so sisi wɔn sibea no nyinaa, Israel anhyehye, gye Hasor nko na Yosua hyeeɛ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na nkuro yi mu asadeɛ nyinaa ne mmoa no deɛ, Israelfoɔ no fom faeɛ; nanso nnipa no deɛ, wɔde nkrantɛ kunkumm wɔn kɔsii sɛ wɔhyee wɔn aseɛ, wɔannya biribiara a ɛhome.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ n’akoa Mose no, saa ara na Mose hyɛɛ Yosua, na saa ara na Yosua yɛeɛ; wanyi asɛm bi amfiri deɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ Mose no nyinaa mu.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Yosua faa asase yi nyinaa, mmepɔ no ne anafoɔ nyinaa ne Gosen asase nyinaa ne ɛpo ho mpaperɛ no ne mpaperɛ so ne Israel mmepɔ ne ɛho asase ta no;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ɛfiri bepɔ a ɛso petee a ɛforo kɔ Seir ho kɔsi Baal-gad, Lebanon bonhwa no mu Hermon bepɔ ase. Na wɔn ahemfo no nyinaa Yosua faa wɔn na ɔbobɔɔ wɔn kunkumm wɔn.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nna bebree na Yosua ne saa ahemfo yi koeɛ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kuro biara nni hɔ a wɔne Israelfoɔ dii asomdwoeɛsɛm, gye Hewifoɔ a wɔte Gibeon no; ɔsa mu na wɔfaa ne nyinaa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɛfiri AWURADE, sɛ ɔpirim wɔn akoma sɛ wɔnkɔhyia Israel ɔko mu, na wɔasɛe wɔn pasapasa na wɔanhu wɔn mmɔbɔ, na mmom wɔasɛe wɔn sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ Mose no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Yosua baa berɛ no mu bɛtwitwaa Anakfoɔ no gu firii mmepɔ no so, firii Hebron, Debir, Anab ne Yuda mmepɔ nyinaa ne Israel mmepɔ nyinaa so, na Yosua sɛee wɔn ne wɔn nkuro nyinaa pasapasa.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Wɔannya Anakfoɔ Israelfoɔ no asase so; gye Gasa ne Gad ne Asdod na ebi kaeɛ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Yosua faa asase no nyinaa, sɛdeɛ AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Mose no nyinaa; na Yosua kyekyɛɛ mu maa Israel maa no yɛɛ wɔn agyapadeɛ, sɛdeɛ wɔn nkyekyɛmu teɛ wɔn mmusuakuo no mu. Na asase no so home firii akodie mu."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na yeinom ne asase no so ahemfo a Israelfoɔ no kunkumm wɔn na wɔdii wɔn asase soɔ wɔ Yordan agya deɛ owiapueeɛ hɔ, firi Arnon subonhwa ho de kɔsi Hermon bepɔ ho ne Araba a ɛwɔ apueeɛ no nyinaa so,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Amorifoɔ hene Sihon a ɔtenaa Hesbon a ɔdii hene firi Aroer a ɛda Arnon subonhwa nsunoa ne subonhwa no mfimfini ne Gilead fa de kɔsi Yabok subonhwa a ɛne Amonfoɔ hyeɛ no ano,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ne Araba so de kɔsi Kinerot po no ano apueeɛ fam, na ɛde kɔsi Araba po no a ɛne Nkyene Po no ano, apueeɛ Bet-yesimot kwan so, ne anafoɔ fam Pisga bepɔ ase no;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ne Basan hene Og a ɔfiri abrane akɛseɛ a aka no mu a ɔtenaa Astarot ne Edrei no asase no.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔdii hene Hermon bepɔ so ne Salka ne Basan nyinaa de kɔsi Gesurfoɔ ne Maakatfoɔ hyeɛ so ne Gilead fa, Hesbon hene Sihon hyeɛ ho.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> AWURADE akoa Mose ne Israelfoɔ no kunkumm wɔn, na AWURADE akoa Mose de asase no maa Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ ne Manase abusuakuo fa no maa wɔdii so.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na yeinom ne asase no so ahemfo a Yosua ne Israelfoɔ no kunkumm wɔn Yordan agya atɔeɛ fam, firi Baal-gad a ɛda Lebanon bonhwa no mu de kɔsi bepɔ a ɛso petee a ɛforo de kɔ Seir no ho; (na Yosua de asase no maa Israel mmusuakuo sɛ wɔnni so sɛdeɛ wɔn nkyekyɛmu no teɛ,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> mmepɔ no so ne ɛpo ho Araba so ne mmepɔ no ase ne ɛserɛ no so ne anafoɔ no: Hetifoɔ, Amorifoɔ ne Kanaanfoɔ, Perisifoɔ, Hewifoɔ ne Yebusifoɔ asase no):",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Yerikohene, Ai a ɛwɔ Betel ho hene,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Yerusalemhene, Hebronhene,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Yarmuthene, Lakishene,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Eglonhene, Geserhene,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Debirhene, Gederhene,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hormahene, Aradhene,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Libnahene, Adulamhene,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Makedahene, Betelhene,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Tapuahene, Heferhene,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Afekhene, Lasaronhene,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Madonhene, Hasorhene,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Simron-meronhene, Aksafhene,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Taanakhene, Megidohene,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kedeshene, Yokneam a ɛwɔ Karmel ase no hene,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Dor a ɛwɔ Dor kokoɔ soɔ hene, amanaman a ɛwɔ Gilgal no hene,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Tirsahene, — ahemfo no nyinaa yɛ aduasa baako."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Yosua abɔ akora na wadi mfeɛ pii; na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Woabɔ akora na woadi mfeɛ pii, na asase a aka sɛ wɔbɛfa no da so dɔɔso bebree.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Asase a aka no nie: Filistifoɔ nsase nyinaa ne Gesur nyinaa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> (Ɛde firi Sihor a ɛwɔ Misraim apueeɛ fam no ano de kɔsi Ekron hyeɛ so atifi fam no, wɔbu ma Kanaanfoɔ. Filistifoɔ ahemfo baanum no: Gasa deɛ ne Asdod deɛ, Askelon deɛ, Gat deɛ ne Ekron deɛ) ne Awifoɔ wɔ anafoɔ fam;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kanaanfoɔ asase no nyinaa ne Meara a ɛyɛ Sidonfoɔ dea no de kɔsi Afek kɔduru Amorifoɔ hyeɛ so;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ne Gebalfoɔ asase ne Lebanon nyinaa wɔ owiapueeɛ de firi Baal-gad a ɛwɔ Hermon bepɔ aseɛ de kɔsi Hamat fam;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> wɔn a wɔte bepɔ no soɔ nyinaa, de firi Lebanon ho de kɔsi Misrefot-maim, Sidonfoɔ nyinaa; me ara, mɛtu wɔn afiri Israelfoɔ no anim; ɛso ntonto nko na twe ma Israel na wɔmfa nni so, sɛdeɛ mehyɛɛ woɔ no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na afei kyɛ asase yi mu na ɛnyɛ mmusuakuo nkron ne Manase abusuakuo fa no agyapadeɛ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Manase fa ne Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ anya wɔn agyapadeɛ a Mose de maa wɔn Yordan agya apueeɛ no, sɛdeɛ AWURADE akoa Mose de maa wɔn no,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ɛfiri Aroer a ɛda Arnon subonhwa no ano no ho ne kuro a ɛda subonhwa no mu no, ne Medeba asaseta no nyinaa kɔsi Dibon,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ne Amorifoɔ hene Sihon a ɔdii hene Hesbon no nkuro no de kɔsi Amonfoɔ hyeɛ so,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ne Gilead ne Gesurfoɔ ne Maakatfoɔ asase ne Hermon bepɔ nyinaa ne Basan nyinaa de kɔsi Salka;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Og a ɔdii hene wɔ Astarot ne Edrei ahennie a ɛwɔ Basan no nyinaa, (ɔno na ɔkaa abrane akɛseɛ no nkaeɛ no mu); na Mose kumm wɔn na ɔtuu wɔn,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> nanso Israelfoɔ antu Gesurfoɔ ne Maakatfoɔ, na Gesurfoɔ ne Maakatfoɔ no tenaa Israel mu de bɛsi nnɛ yi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Lewi abusuakuo no nko na wamma wɔn agyapadeɛ bie. AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn gya afɔdeɛ so adeɛ no, ɛno ne n’agyapadeɛ, sɛdeɛ ɔka kyerɛɛ no no.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Mose de maa Ruben mma abusuakuo no sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na wɔn hyeɛ no firi Aroer a ɛda Arnon subonhwa no ano no ho ne kuro a ɛda subonhwa no mu ne Medeba ho asaseta no nyinaa.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hesbon ne ne nkuro a ɛdeda asaseta soɔ no nyinaa. Dibon ne Bamot-baal ne Bet-baal-meon",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ne Yahas ne Kedemot ne Mefaat",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ne Kiriataim ne Sibma ne Seret-sahar, bonhwa no mu bepɔ so",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ne Bet-peor ne Pisga bepɔ ase ne Bet-yesimot,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> asaseta no nkuro no nyinaa; ne Amorifoɔ hene Sihon a ɔdii hene Hesbon no ahennie nyinaa; ɔno na Mose kumm no ne Midian mmapɔmma, Ewi ne Rekem ne Sur ne Hur ne Reba, Sihon asafohene a wɔtenaa asase no soɔ no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Beor ba Bileam, nkɔmhyɛfoɔ no nso, Israelfoɔ de nkrantɛ kumm no fraa atɔfoɔ no mu.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Ruben mma no hyeɛ ne Yordan ne ɛho hyeɛ. Yei ne Ruben mma no agyapadeɛ sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ, nkuro no ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Mose de maa Gad abusuakuo, Gadfoɔ no, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wɔn hyeɛ ne Yaser ne Gilead nkuro no nyinaa, ne Amonfoɔ asase fa, de kɔsi Aroer a ɛda Raba anim no,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na ɛfiri Hesbon de kɔsi Ramat-mispe ne Betonim, na ɛde firi Mahanaim de kɔsi Debir hyeɛ so;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ne bonhwa no mu, Bet-haram ne Bet-nimra ne Sukot ne Safon a ɛyɛ Hesbon hene Sihon ahennie no nkaeɛ, Yordan ne ɛho hyeɛ, de kɔsi Kineret po no awieeɛ, Yordan agya apueeɛ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Yei ne Gadfoɔ agyapadeɛ sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ, nkuro no ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na Mose maa Manase abusuakuo fa no nso bi, na ɛyɛɛ Manase abusuakuo fa no deɛ sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na wɔn hyeɛ firi Mahanaim, Basan nyinaa, Basan hene Og ahennie nyinaa ne Yair nkuro a ɛwɔ Basan no nyinaa, nkuro aduosia;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> ne Gilead fa ne Astarot ne Edrei, Og ahennie nkuro a ɛwɔ Basan no. Wɔde maa Manase ba Makir mma, sɛ ɛnyɛ Makir mma fa dea, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Yei ne agyapadeɛ a Mose kyekyɛɛ wɔ Moab mpaperɛ soɔ, Yeriko, Yordan agya apueeɛ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na Lewi abusuakuo no deɛ, Mose amma wɔn agyapadeɛ biara: AWURADE, Israel Nyankopɔn, ɔno ne wɔn agyapadeɛ, sɛdeɛ ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn no."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na yei ne Israel agyapadeɛ a wɔnyaa no Kanaan asase soɔ a Ɔsɔfoɔ Eleasa ne Nun ba Yosua ne Israelfoɔ mmusuakuo mu agyanom so atitire no kyekyɛ maa wɔn,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> wɔn agyapadeɛ a ɛnam ntontotwe soɔ, sɛdeɛ AWURADE nam Mose so hyɛɛ sɛ wɔmma mmusuakuo nkron ne fa no.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Mose ama mmusuakuo mmienu ne fa no agyapadeɛ wɔ Yordan agya, na Lewifoɔ deɛ, wamma wɔn agyapadeɛ biara wɔ wɔn mu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Yosef mma yɛ mmusuakuo mmienu, Manase ne Efraim, na wɔamma Lewifoɔ no kyɛfa biara asase no so, gye nkuro a wɔbɛtena mu ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase ma wɔn mmoa ne wɔn nnoɔma.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ Mose no, saa na Israelfoɔ no yɛeɛ, na wɔkyɛɛ asase no mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Yudafoɔ no baa Yosua nkyɛn wɔ Gilgal; na Kenesini Yefune ba Kaleb ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Wo ara wonim me ne wo ho asɛm a AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Nyankopɔn nipa Mose wɔ Kades-barnea.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Medii mfirinhyia aduanan na AWURADE akoa Mose somaa me firi Kades-barnea sɛ menkɔsra asase no, na mesane mede emu asɛm mebrɛɛ no, sɛdeɛ ɛwɔ m’akoma mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na me nuanom a wɔne me foro kɔeɛ no maa ɔman no akoma tui, na me deɛ, medii AWURADE me Nyankopɔn akyi mewiee.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Mose kaa ntam da no ara sɛ: Asase a wo nan tiaa soɔ no bɛyɛ wo ne wo mma agyapadeɛ daa, ɛfiri sɛ woadi AWURADE me Nyankopɔn akyi awie.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na afei hwɛ, AWURADE ama matena ase sɛdeɛ ɔkaeɛ no, mfirinhyia aduanan nnum yi, ɛfiri berɛ a AWURADE kaa asɛm yi kyerɛɛ Mose berɛ a na Israel nam serɛ soɔ no. Na afei, hwɛ, ɛnnɛ madi mfirinhyia aduɔwɔtwe nnum.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Meda so mewɔ ahoɔden nnɛ yi ara, sɛ deɛ na meteɛ da a Mose somaa me no; sɛdeɛ m’ahoɔden teɛ da no, saa ara na ɛteɛ nnɛ ma ɔko ne adifire ne emuba.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na afei, fa bepɔ yi a AWURADE kaa ho asɛm da no no ma me, ɛfiri sɛ da no ara wotee sɛ Anakfoɔ ne nkuro akɛseɛ a wɔatoto ho afasuo wɔ hɔ. Ebia AWURADE bɛdi m’akyi na matu wɔn, sɛdeɛ AWURADE kaeɛ no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Yosua hyiraa no, na ɔde Hebron maa Yefune ba Kaleb sɛ n’agyapadeɛ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ɛno nti na Hebron yɛɛ Kenesini Yefune ba Kaleb agyapadeɛ de bɛsi nnɛ da yi, ɛfiri sɛ ɔdii AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn no akyi yie.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nso akane no na Hebron din ne Kiriat-arba. Arba yi ne Anakfoɔ mu nipa kɛseɛ koraa. Na asase no so dwo firii akodie mu."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Yuda mma abusuakuo ntonto no, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ no, ɛtɔɔ Edom hyeɛ ho kɔduruu Sin serɛ so, wɔ anafoɔ fam asase a ɛyɛ anafoɔ hyeɛ no awieeɛ so.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na wɔn anafoɔ fam hyeɛ no firi Nkyene Po awieeɛ no ho dɔnnɔn a ɛbu fa anafoɔ fam no ano.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɛnam Akrabim aforoeɛ anafoɔ fam sene kɔ Sin, na ɛforo kɔ anafoɔ fam wɔ Kades-barnea, na ɛtwam kɔ Hesron, na ɛforo kɔ Adar, na ɛpono kɔ Karka.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɛtwam kɔ Asmon, na ɛkɔpue Misraim subonhwa no ano, na ɛkɔpem mpoano. Yei nyɛ mo anafoɔ fam hyeɛ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na apueeɛ hyeɛ ne Nkyene Po no de bɛsi Yordan awieeɛ. Na atifi fam hyeɛ no firi Nkyene Po ho dɔnnɔn a ɛwɔ Yordan awieeɛ no ho.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no foro Bet-hogla, na ɛsene fa Bet-araba atifi fam, na ɛhyeɛ no foro kɔsi Ruben ba Bohan boɔ no ho.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no firi Akor bonhwa no mu foro kɔ Debir, na ɛdane kɔ atifi fam kyerɛ Gilgal a ɛda Adumim aforoeɛ a ɛwɔ subonhwa no anafoɔ fam ntentensoɔ no. Na ɛhyeɛ no twam fa En-semes nsuo no ano, na ɛkɔpem En-rogel.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no foro fa Hinom ba bonhwa no mu, Yebusifoɔ nkyɛn mu anafoɔ fam, (ɛne Yerusalem); na ɛhyeɛ no foro kɔ bepɔ a ɛwɔ Hinom bonhwa no ntentensoɔ wɔ atɔeɛ wɔ Refaim bonhwa no atifi fam awieeɛ no atifi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no hima firi bepɔ no mpampam kɔ Neftoa asutire no ho, na ɛfiri hɔ kɔ Efron bepɔ so nkuro ho, na ɛhyeɛ no hima kɔ Baala (a ɛne Kiriat-yearim).",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no konton firi Baala kɔ atɔeɛ, Seir bepɔ ho, na ɛsene kɔ Har-yearim, (ɛne Kesalon), nkyɛn mu wɔ atifi fam; na ɛsiane kɔ Bet-semes, na ɛsene kɔ Timna;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na ɛhyeɛ no pue kɔ Ekron nkyɛn mu atifi fam na ɛhima kɔ Sikron, na ɛtwam kɔ Baala bepɔ no so, na ɛpue kɔ Yabneel; na ɛhyeɛ no kɔpem ɛpo no ano.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na atɔeɛ hyeɛ no ne ɛpo kɛseɛ no ne ɛho hyeɛ. Yeinom ne Yudafoɔ no hyeɛ a atwa ahyia sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Yefune ba Kaleb deɛ, ɔmaa no kyɛfa, Yudafoɔ no mu sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ Yosua no: (Anak agya Arba) kuro a ɛne Hebron.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Kaleb tuu Anak mma baasa no firii hɔ, Sesai ne Ahiman ne Talmai, Anak asefoɔ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔfiri hɔ foro kɔɔ Debirfoɔ ho; nso akane no na Debir din ne Kiriat-sefer.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Kaleb kaa sɛ: Deɛ ɔbɛbɔ Kiriat-sefer na ɔbɛfa no, mede me babaa Aksa bɛma no aware.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛnna Kaleb nua Kenas ba Otniel kɔfaeɛ, na ɔde ne babaa Aksa maa no awareɛ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔbaa no kɔɔ Otniel nkyɛn no, ɔhyɛɛ Otniel sɛ ɔmmisa n’agya Kaleb hɔ asase bi; na ɔbaa no firi n’afunumu so sii fam; na Kaleb ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na worehwehwɛ?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Ma me akyɛdeɛ bi ɛ, na anafoɔ asase na wode ama me nti, ma me mmasuo nso. Na ɔmaa no atifi mmasuo ne anafoɔ mmasuo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Yei ne Yuda mma abusuakuo no agyapadeɛ, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Yudafoɔ abusuakuo no nkuro a ɛdeda anafoɔ fam pɛɛ de rekɔ Edom hyeɛ soɔ ne: Kabseel ne Eder ne Yagur,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> ne Kina ne Dimona ne Adada",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ne Kedes ne Hasor ne Itnan,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Sif ne Telem ne Bealot,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> ne Hasor-hadata ne Keriot-hesron, (ɛne Hasor),",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Amam ne Sema ne Molada",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ne Hasar-gada ne Hesmon ne Bet-pelet,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ne Hasar-sual ne Beer-seba ne ɛho nkuraa,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Baala ne Iyim ne Esem,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ne Eltolad ne Kesil ne Horma,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> ne Siklag ne Madmana ne Sansana,",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ne Lebaot ne Silhim ne Ain ne Rimon: Ne nyinaa yɛ nkuro aduonu nkron ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ɛpo ho mpaperɛ so deɛ ne: Estaol ne Sora ne Asna,",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> ne Sanoa ne En-ganim, Tapua ne Enam,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Yarmut ne Adulam, Soko ne Aseka,",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> ne Saaraim ne Aditaim ne Gedera ne Gederotaim: Nkuro dunan ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Senan ne Hadasa ne Migdal-gad",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> ne Dilean ne Mispe ne Yokteel,",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Lakis ne Boskat ne Eglon,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> ne Kabon ne Lahmam ne Kitlis,",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> ne Gederot, Bet-dagon ne Naama ne Makeda: Nkuro dunsia ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Libna ne Eter ne Asan,",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> ne Yifta ne Asna ne Nesib",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> ne Keila ne Aksib ne Maresa: Nkuro nkron ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Ekron ne ɛho nkuro ne nkuraa,",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> ɛfiri Ekron de kɔsi ɛpo fam deɛ ɛwɔ Asdod nkyɛn mu nyinaa ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Asdod, ɛho nkuro ne nkuraa, Gasa, ɛho nkuro ne nkuraa de kɔsi Misraim subonhwa no ano, ne Ɛpo Kɛseɛ ne ɛho hyeɛ.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Na mmepɔ so deɛ ne: Samir ne Yatir ne Soko,",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> ne Dana ne Kiriat-sana (a ɛne Debir),",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> ne Anab ne Estemo ne Anim,",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> ne Gosen ne Holon ne Gilo: Nkuro dubaako ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Arab ne Duma ne Esan,",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> ne Yanum ne Bet-tapua ne Afeka",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> ne Humta ne Kiriat-arba (a ɛne Hebron), ne Sior: Nkuro nkron ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Maon, Karmel ne Sif ne Yuta,",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> ne Yesreel ne Yokdeam ne Sanoa,",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Kain, Gibea ne Timna: Nkuro du ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Halhul, Bet-sur ne Gedor,",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> ne Maarat ne Bet-anot ne Eltekon: Nkuro nsia ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Kiriat-baal (a ɛne Kiriat-yearim), ne Raba: Nkuro mmienu ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Ɛserɛ so deɛ ne: Bet-araba, Midin ne Sekaka",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> ne Nibsan ne Nkyene Kuro no ne En-gedi: Nkuro nsia ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> Na Yebusifoɔ a wɔte Yerusalem no deɛ, Yudafoɔ no antumi antu wɔn, na Yebusifoɔ no ne Yudafoɔ no tenaa Yerusalem de bɛduru nnɛ yi."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na deɛ ntonto no yi maa Yosef mma no firi Yeriko Yordan ano, Yeriko asuo apueeɛ, ɛserɛ a ɛfiri Yeriko kɔ Betel bepɔ soɔ no;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> na ɛfiri Betel de kɔ Lus, na ɛtwam kɔ Arkifoɔ hyeɛ so wɔ Atarot,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ɛsiane kɔ atɔeɛ, Yafletifoɔ hyeɛ ho de kɔsi anafoɔ Bet-horon hyeɛ so, na ɛde kɔ Geser, na ɛkɔpem mpoano.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Yosef mma Manase ne Efraim nyaa wɔn agyapadeɛ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Efraimfoɔ no hyeɛ sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ nie: Wɔn agyapadeɛ hyeɛ ne Atarot-adar apueeɛ de kɔsi atifi wɔ Bet-horon;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na ɛhyeɛ no firi hɔ kɔ atɔeɛ wɔ Mikmetat, atifi fam, na ɛkonton kɔ apueeɛ wɔ Taanat-silo, na ɛsiane ho kɔ Yanoa apueeɛ,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na ɛfiri Yanoa siane kɔ Atarot ne Naarat, na ɛka Yeriko, na ɛkɔpem Yordan ano.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛhyeɛ no firi Tapua kɔ atɔeɛ kɔsi Kana subonhwa mu, na ɛkɔpem mpoano. Yei ne Efraimfoɔ abusuakuo no agyapadeɛ sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ne nkuro a wɔyiyi maa Efraimfoɔ wɔ Manasefoɔ agyapadeɛ mu no, nkuro no nyinaa ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Nanso wɔantu Kanaanfoɔ a wɔte Geser no, na Kanaanfoɔ no atena Efraim mu de abɛduru nnɛ, na wɔayɛ nkoa a wɔde ɔsom adwuma yi toɔ."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ntonto no yii Manase abusuakuo deɛ, ɛfiri sɛ ɔno ne Yosef abakan. Manase abakan Makir a ɔyɛ Gilead agya no nyaa Gilead ne Basan, ɛfiri sɛ ɔyɛ dɔmmarima.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɛyii Manase mma a aka no deɛ, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ, Abi-eser mma ne Helek mma ne Asriel mma ne Sekem mma ne Hefer mma ne Semida mma; yeinom ne Yosef ba Manase mmammarima sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Manase ba Makir ba Gilead ba Hefer ba Selofehad no nni mmammarima, na mmammaa na ɔwɔ. Na yeinom ne ne mma mmaa no din, Mahla, Noa, Hogla, Milka ne Tirsa.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔbaa Ɔsɔfoɔ Eleasa ne Nun ba Yosua ne mmapɔmma no anim bɛkaa sɛ: AWURADE hyɛɛ Mose sɛ ɔmma yɛn agyapadeɛ, yɛn nuammarimanom mu. Na ɔnam AWURADE anomu asɛm no so maa wɔn agyapadeɛ wɔn agya nuanom no mu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Manase nkyekyɛmu a ɔnyaeɛ no yɛ du, ɛsono Gilead ne Basan asase a ɛwɔ Yordan agya no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Manase mmammaa no nyaa agyapadeɛ wɔ ne mmammarimanom no mu, na Gilead asase no yɛɛ Manase mma nkaeɛ no deɛ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Manase hyeɛ no firi Aser kɔ Mikmetat a ɛda Sekem apueeɛ no, na ɛhyeɛ no kɔ anafoɔ fam, En-tapuafoɔ no ho.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tapua asase yɛɛ Manase deɛ, na Tapua kuro a ɛwɔ Manase hyeɛ soɔ no yɛ Efraimfoɔ no deɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no siane kɔ Kana subonhwa no ho, subonhwa no anafoɔ fam. Ɛhɔ nkuro a ɛyɛ Manase nkuro no yɛɛ Efraim deɛ. Na Manase hyeɛ no wɔ subonhwa no atifi fam, na ano kɔka mpoano.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Anafoɔ fam no yɛɛ Efraim deɛ, na atifi fam deɛ yɛɛ Manase deɛ, na ɛpo no ne ɛhyeɛ. Na wɔne Aser bɔɔ hyeɛ atifi fam, na wɔne Isakar bɔɔ no apueeɛ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na nkuro a Manase nyaa no Isakar ne Aser ntam ne Bet-sean ne ɛho nkuro ne Yibleam ne ɛho nkuro ne wɔn a wɔte Dor ne ɛho nkuro ne En-dorfoɔ ne ɛho nkuro ne Taanakfoɔ ne ɛho nkuro ne Megidofoɔ ne ɛho nkuro, nkokoɔ mmiɛnsa so amantoɔ no.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Nanso Manasefoɔ antumi antu nkuro no mufoɔ, na Kanaanfoɔ no pɛɛ asase no so tena.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Israelfoɔ ho yɛɛ den no, wɔmaa Kanaanfoɔ no de ɔsom adwuma yii toɔ, na tuo deɛ, wɔantu wɔn.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Yosef mma no bɛka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Ɛnam deɛn so na woma me agyapadeɛ ntonto baako ne susuhoma baako? Na me deɛ, meyɛ ɔman kɛseɛ, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE ahyira me de abɛduru sɛsɛɛ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ woyɛ ɔman kɛseɛ a, foro kɔ kwaeɛ no mu kɔbu hɔ fa, Perisifoɔ ne abrane no asase so, ɛfiri sɛ wonsene Efraim mmepɔ so.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Yosef mma no kaa sɛ: Bepɔ no nso yɛn, nso Kanaanfoɔ a wɔte mpaperɛ mu hɔ nyinaa wɔ dadeɛ nteaseɛnam, wɔn a wɔte Bet-sean ne ɛho nkuro mu ne wɔn a wɔte Yesreel bonhwa no mu nyinaa.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ Yosef fie, Efraim ne Manase sɛ: Ɔman kɛseɛ ne wo, na wowɔ ahoɔden kɛseɛ, ɛnyɛ ntonto baako pɛ na wobɛnya,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na mmom bepɔ no nyɛ wo deɛ; ɛwom sɛ ɛyɛ kwaeɛ deɛ, nanso bu fa, kɔsi deɛ ano bɛka. Na Kanaanfoɔ no, sɛ wɔwɔ dadeɛ nteaseɛnam na wɔyɛ ahoɔdenfoɔ mpo a, wobɛtu wɔn."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Israelfoɔ asafo no nyinaa bɛhyiaa Silo, na wɔsii ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no wɔ hɔ, na wɔbrɛɛ asase no ase wɔn anim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na aka Israelfoɔ no mu wɔn a wɔnkyɛɛ agyapadeɛ mmaa wɔn no, mmusuakuo nson.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ Israelfoɔ no sɛ: Da bɛn na mobɛtwentwɛn mo nan ase akɔsie ansa na moakɔ akɔfa asase a AWURADE mo agyanom Nyankopɔn de ama mo no?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Montu abusuakuo biara mu nnipa baasa, na mensoma wɔn mma wɔnsɔre nkɔkyini asase no so, na wɔntwerɛ ho asɛm, sɛ ɛbɛyɛ na ɛbɛyɛ wɔn agyapadeɛ, na wɔmmra me nkyɛn.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na monkyekyɛ mu nkyekyɛmu nson. Yuda nnyina ne hyeɛ so anafoɔ fam, na Yosef fie nnyina wɔn hyeɛ so atifi fam.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na montwerɛ asase no nkyekyɛmu nson no ho asɛm, na momfa mmrɛ me ha, na mentwe ntonto memma mo AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn anim ha.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Lewifoɔ rennya mo mu kyɛfa, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE asɔfodie no ne wɔn agyapadeɛ. Na Gad ne Ruben ne Manase abusuakuo fa no anya wɔn agyapadeɛ, Yordan agya apueeɛ a AWURADE akoa Mose de maa wɔn no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛnna mmarima no sɔre kɔeɛ; na Yosua hyɛɛ wɔn a wɔrekɔ akɔtwerɛ asase no ho asɛm no sɛ: Monkɔ nkɔkyini asase no so na montwerɛ ho asɛm, na monsane mmra me nkyɛn, na mentwe ntonto memma mo, AWURADE anim ha wɔ Silo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na mmarima no sii mu kɔ kɔfaa asase no so, na wɔtwerɛɛ no sɛdeɛ nkuro no teteɛ nkyekyɛmu nson de hyɛɛ nwoma bi mu, na wɔsane baa Yosua nkyɛn Silo nsraban mu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Yosua twee ntonto maa wɔn AWURADE anim wɔ Silo, na Yosua kyɛɛ asase no mu wɔ hɔ maa Israelfoɔ no sɛdeɛ wɔn nkyekyɛmu teɛ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Benyaminfoɔ abusuakuo ntonto bae sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ; na wɔn ntonto no hyeɛ firi Yuda mma ne Yosef mma ntam.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔn atifi fam hyeɛ firi Yordan; na ɛhyeɛ no foro fa Yeriko nkyɛn mu atifi fam, na ɛforo kɔ bepɔ no so kɔ atɔeɛ, na ano kɔduru Bet-awen serɛ so.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no firi hɔ sene fa anafoɔ fam kɔ Lus, wɔ Lus a ɛne Betel no nkyɛn mu, na ɛhyeɛ no siane kɔ Atarot-adar, bepɔ a ɛda anafoɔ Bet-horon anafoɔ fam no so.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no hima na ɛkonton kɔ atɔeɛ fam fa bepɔ a ɛda Bet-horon ntentensoɔ anafoɔ fam no anafoɔ fam, na ano kɔduru Kiriat-baal (a ɛne Kiriat-yearim), Yuda mma kuro bi. Atɔeɛ fam deɛ ne no.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na anafoɔ fam deɛ firi Kiriat-yearim kurotia, na ɛhyeɛ no firi hɔ kɔ atɔeɛ, na ɛkɔ Neftoa asutire ho.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no siane kɔ bepɔ a ɛda Hinom ba bonhwa anim a ɛwɔ Refaim bonhwa mu atifi fam no ano nohoa, na ɛsiane Hinom bonhwa no kɔ Yebusifoɔ anafoɔ fam nkyɛn mu, na ɛsiane kɔ En-rogel ho.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɛhima kɔ atifi fam, na ɛfiri hɔ kɔ En-semes, na ɛfiri hɔ kɔ Gelilot a ɛda Adumim aforoeɛ no ntentensoɔ, na ɛsiane kɔ Ruben ba Bohan boɔ no ho.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɛtwam fa atifi fam nkyɛn mu Araba ntentensoɔ, na ɛsiane kɔ Araba.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no twam kɔ Bet-hogla atifi fam nkyɛn mu, na ano kɔduru Nkyene Po atifi fam dɔnnɔn no ho, Yordan anafoɔ fam awieeɛ. Yei ne anafoɔ fam hyeɛ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Yordan ne n’apueeɛ fam hyeɛ. Yei ne Benyaminfoɔ agyapadeɛ sɛdeɛ n’ahyeɛ teteɛ de hyia, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Benyaminfoɔ abusuakuo, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ no nkuro nie: Yeriko ne Bet-hogla ne Emek-kesis,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> ne Bet-araba ne Semaraim ne Betel,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ne Awim ne Para ne Ofra,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ne Kefar-amonai ne Ofni ne Geba: Nkuro dummienu ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Gibeon ne Rama ne Beerot,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> ne Mispe ne Kefira ne Mosa,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ne Rekem ne Yirpeel ne Tarala,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ne Sela, Ha-elef ne Yebus a ɛne Yerusalem, Gibeat, Kiriat: Nkuro dunan ne ɛho nkuraa. Yei ne Benyaminfoɔ no agyapadeɛ sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ntonto a ɛtɔ so mmienu no ba maa Simeon, Simeonfoɔ abusuakuo no, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ; na wɔn agyapadeɛ da Yuda mma agyapadeɛ ntam.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na deɛ wɔnyaa no wɔn agyapadeɛ mu ne Beer-seba, Seba, Molada,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hasar-sual, Bala, Asem,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Eltolad, Betul, Horma,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Siklag, Bet-markabot, Hasar-susa,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bet-lebaot ne Saruhen: Nkuro dummiɛnsa ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ain, Rimon, Eter ne Asan: Nkuro nnan ne ɛho nkuraa;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ne nkuraa a ɛdeda nkuro yi ho hyia de kɔsi Baalat-beer nyinaa, Ramat a ɛda Negeb. Yei ne Simeon mma abusuakuo no agyapadeɛ sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Yudafoɔ kyɛfa no bi na ɛyɛɛ Simeonfoɔ agyapadeɛ, ɛfiri sɛ Yudafoɔ kyɛfa no boroo wɔn so, enti Simeonfoɔ nyaa agyapadeɛ wɔn agyapadeɛ no mu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na tonto a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa no ba maa Sebulon sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ. Na wɔn agyapadeɛ hyeɛ kɔduruu Sarid.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔn hyeɛ no foro kɔ atɔeɛ wɔ Marala, na ɛkɔpem Dabeset, na ɛkɔpem subonhwa a ɛwɔ Yokneam apueeɛ fam no ano.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɛsane firi Sarid kɔ anim owiapueeɛ de kɔ Kislot-tabor hyeɛ so na ɛfiri adi kɔ Daberat, na ɛforo kɔ Yafia.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɛfiri hɔ twam kɔ apueeɛ de kɔ Gat-hefer, Et-kasin, na ɛfiri Rimon a ɛhima de kɔ Nea.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no konton kɔ atifi fam de kɔ Hanaton, na ano kɔduru Yifta-el bonhwa no mu;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ne Katat ne Nahalal ne Simron ne Yidala ne Betlehem: Nkuro dummienu ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Yei ne Sebulon mma agyapadeɛ sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ: Nkuro no ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ntonto a ɛtɔ so nnan no ba maa Isakar, Isakarfoɔ no, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na wɔn hyeɛ kɔɔ Yesreel, Kesulot, Sunem,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hafraim, Sihon, Anaharat,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Rabit, Kision, Abes,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Remet, En-ganim, En-hada ne Bet-pases.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no kɔpem Tabor, Sahasima ne Bet-semes, na wɔn hyeɛ no ano kɔduru Yordan ano: Nkuro dunsia ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Yei ne Isakarfoɔ abusuakuo no agyapadeɛ, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ: Nkuro no ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ntonto a ɛtɔ so nnum no ba maa Aserfoɔ abusuakuo no, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wɔn hyeɛ ne Helkat, Hali, Beten, Aksaf,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Alamelek, Amad, ne Misal na ɛkɔpem Karmel wɔ atɔeɛ, ne Sihor-libnat.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ɛsane kɔ owiapueeɛ de kɔ Bet-dagon, na ɛkɔpem Sebulon ne Yifta-el bonhwa mu, Bet-emek ne Neiel atifi fam, na ɛfiri adi kɔ Kabul atifi fam,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ebron, Rehob, Hamon, ne Kana de kɔsi Sidon Kɛseɛ.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no dane kɔ Rama kɔduru kuro denden Tiro, na ɛhyeɛ no dane kɔ Hosa, na ano kɔpem ɛpo no Aksib fam,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ne Uma ne Afek ne Rehob: Nkuro aduonu mmienu ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ɛno ne Aserfoɔ abusuakuo agyapadeɛ sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ: Nkuro no ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Naftalifoɔ na ntonto a ɛtɔ so nsia no ba maa wɔn, Naftalifoɔ no, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na wɔn hyeɛ firi Helef, Saananim dupɔn no ho ne Adami-nekeb ne Yabneel de kɔ Lakum, na ano kɔpem Yordan.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no dane kɔ atɔeɛ wɔ Asnot-tabor, na ɛfiri hɔ kɔ Hukok, na ɛkɔpem Sebulon anafoɔ fam, ne Aser wɔ atɔeɛ, ne Yuda wɔ apueeɛ, Yordan ano.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na nkuro a wɔatoto ho afasuo nie: Sidim, Ser, Hamat, Rakat, Kineret,",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Adama, Rama, Hasor,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kedes, Edrei, En-hasor,",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Yiron, Midgal-el, Horem, Bet-anat ne Bet-semes: Nkuro dunkron ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Yei ne Naftalifoɔ abusuakuo no agyapadeɛ, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ: Nkuro no ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Dan mma abusuakuo no, sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ na ntonto a ɛtɔ so nson no ba maa wɔn.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Na wɔn agyapadeɛ hyeɛ ne: Sora, Estaol, Ir-semes,",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Saalabin, Ayalon, Yitla,",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Elon, Timna, Ekron,",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Elteke, Gibeton, Baalat,",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Yehud, Bene-berak, Gat-rimon,",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Me-yarkon, Rakon, ɛne Yafo anim hyeɛ no.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Na Danfoɔ firii hɔ kɔnyaa ɛhyeɛ foforɔ bi, ɛfiri sɛ Danfoɔ no foro kɔe ne Lesem kɔkoe, na wɔfae, na wɔde nkrantɛ ano sɛee no, na wɔdii so, na wɔtenaa hɔ, na wɔfrɛɛ Lesem sɛ Dan, sɛdeɛ wɔn agya Dan din teɛ.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Ɛno ne Danfoɔ abusuakuo agyapadeɛ sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ: Nkuro no ne ɛho nkuraa.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Na wɔwiee asase no mu kyɛ sɛdeɛ n’ahyeɛ no teɛ no, Israelfoɔ maa Nun ba Yosua agyapadeɛ wɔ wɔn mu,",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> AWURADE anomu asɛm so na wɔmaa no kuro a ɔbisaeɛ no, ɛne Timnat-sera a ɛda Efraim bepɔ soɔ, na ɔkyekyeree kuro no tenaa mu.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Yeinom ne agyapadeɛ a Ɔsɔfoɔ Eleasa ne Nun ba Yosua ne Israelfoɔ mmusuakuo agyanom mu atitire no de ntonto kyɛɛ mu wɔ Silo, AWURADE anim, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano. Na wɔwiee asase no mu kyɛ."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ka kyerɛ Israelfoɔ no sɛ: Monyi dwanekɔbea nkuro a menam Mose so mekaa mo ho asɛm no,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na onipakumfoɔ a ɔbɛkum obi nsapa mu anaa wammoapa no nnwane nkɔ hɔ, na ɛnyɛ mo dwanekɔbea mfiri mogya ho werefoɔ nsam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na deɛ ɔdwane kɔ saa nkuro yi bi mu no nnyina kuro no pono ano, na ɔnka ne nsɛm ngu kuro no mu mpanimfoɔ aso mu, na wɔmfa no nkɔ wɔn nkyɛn, kuro no mu, na wɔmma no tenabea na ɔne wɔn ntena.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na sɛ mogya ho werefoɔ no ti no ba a, wɔmmfa onipakumfoɔ no nnhyɛ ne nsa, ɛfiri sɛ na ɔnnim na ɔbɔɔ ne yɔnko no, nanso berɛ a atwam no na ɔntane no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔntena kuro no mu nkɔsi sɛ ɔbɛgyina asafo no anim na wɔabu no atɛn, kɔsi sɛ ɔsɔfo panin a ɔwɔ so saa berɛ no bɛwuo; ɛno ansa na onipakumfoɔ no nsane nkɔ ne kurom ne ne fie, na ɔnkɔ kuro a ɔfiri mu dwaneeɛ no mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛnna wɔyiyii Kedes wɔ Galilea, Naftali bepɔ so, Sekem wɔ Efraim bepɔ so, ne Kiriat-arba (a ɛne Hebron) wɔ Yuda bepɔ so.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Yordan agya, Yeriko apueeɛ nso wɔyii Beser, ɛserɛ so asaseta so de firii Ruben abusuakuo mu, na Ramot wɔ Gilead de firii Gad abusuakuo mu, ne Golan wɔ Basan de firii Manase abusuakuo mu mae.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Yeinom ne nkuro a wɔyiyi totoo hɔ maa Israelfoɔ nyinaa ne ɔhɔhoɔ a wabɛsoɛ wɔn mu, sɛ obiara a ɔkum ɔkra bi nsapa mu no nnwane nkɔ hɔ na wanwu mogya ho werefoɔ nsam de kɔsi sɛ ɔbɛgyina asafo no anim."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Lewifoɔ agyanom atitire baa Ɔsɔfoɔ Eleasa ne Nun ba Yosua ne Israelfoɔ mmusuakuo agyanom atitire nkyɛn,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> na wɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn Silo, Kanaan asase so sɛ: AWURADE nam Mose so hyɛɛ sɛ wɔmma yɛn nkuro ntena mu ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase mma yɛn mmoa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Israelfoɔ nam AWURADE anomu asɛm so de wɔn agyapadeɛ mu nkuro yi ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase maa Lewifoɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ntonto no ba maa Kohatfoɔ mmusua, na Ɔsɔfoɔ Aaron mma a wɔfiri Lewifoɔ mu no nam tonto so nyaa Yuda abusuakuo ne Simeon abusuakuo ne Benyamin abusuakuo mu nkuro dummiɛnsa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Kohatfoɔ a wɔkaeɛ no nam ntonto so nyaa Efraim abusuakuo mmusua ne Dan abusuakuo ne Manase abusuakuo fa no mu nkuro du.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Gersonfoɔ no nam ntonto so nyaa Isakar abusuakuo mmusua ne Aser abusuakuo ne Naftali abusuakuo ne Manase abusuakuo fa a ɛwɔ Basan no mu nkuro dummiɛnsa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Merari mma sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ no, wɔnyaa Ruben abusuakuo ne Gad abusuakuo ne Sebulon abusuakuo mu nkuro dummienu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no nam ntonto so de nkuro yi ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase maa Lewifoɔ no, sɛdeɛ AWURADE nam Mose nsa so hyɛeɛ no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wɔde Yudafoɔ abusuakuo ne Simeonfoɔ abusuakuo mu nkuro a wɔbɛbobɔ din yi mae.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɛba maa Aaron mma a wɔfiri Kohatfoɔ mmusua mu, Lewifoɔ no mu no, ɛfiri sɛ wɔn deɛ ne ntonto a ɛdi kan no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔde Kiriat-arba, (Anak agya Arba) ne kuro a ɛne Hebron a ɛwɔ Yuda bepɔ soɔ ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase a ɛtwa ho hyia no maa wɔn.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na kuro no ho mfofowa ne nkuraa no deɛ, wɔde maa Yefune ba Kaleb agyapadeɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Ɔsɔfoɔ Aaron mma no, wɔde nnipakumfoɔ dwanekɔbea kuro Hebron ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase maa wɔn ne Libna ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ne Yatir ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase ne Estemoa ne ɛho asase,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ne Holon ne ɛho asase ne Debir ne ɛho asase,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ne Ain ne ɛho asase, ne Yuta ne ɛho asase, ne Bet-semes ne ɛho asase: Mmusuakuo mmienu yi mu nkuro nkron.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Benyamin abusuakuo mu deɛ, wɔde Gibeon ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase, ne Geba ne ɛho asase,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ne Anatot ne ɛho asase, ne Almon ne ɛho asase mae: Nkuro nnan.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Aaron mma asɔfoɔ no nkuro nyinaa yɛ nkuro dummiɛnsa ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Kehat mma Lewifoɔ no, Kehat mma nkaeɛ no mmusua no, wɔn ntonto nkuro firii Efraim abusuakuo mu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Wɔde nnipakumfoɔ dwanekɔbea kuro Sekem ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase maa wɔn, Efraim bepɔ so, ne Geser ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> ne Kibsaim ne ɛho asase ne Bet-horon ne ɛho asase: Nkuro nnan;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ne Dan abusuakuo mu Elteke ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase, Gibeton ne ɛho asase,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ayalon ne ɛho asase ne Gat-rimon ne ɛho asase: Nkuro nnan;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> ne Manase abusuakuo fa no mu, Taanak ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase ne Gat-rimon ne ɛho asase: Nkuro mmienu.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Nkuro a ɛyɛɛ Kehat mma nkaeɛ no mmusua no deɛ nyinaa yɛ nkuro du ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na Gerson mma a wɔfiri Lewifoɔ mmusua no mu no, wɔmaa wɔn Manase abusuakuo fa no mu nnipakumfoɔ dwanekɔbea kuro Golan wɔ Basan ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase ne Beestra ne ɛho asase: Nkuro mmienu;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ne Isakar abusuakuo mu, Kision ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase, Daberat ne ɛho asase,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Yarmut ne ɛho asase, En-ganim ne ɛho asase: Nkuro nnan,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ne Aser abusuakuo mu: Misal ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase, Abdon ne ɛho asase,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Helkat ne ɛho asase, ne Rehob ne ɛho asase: Nkuro nnan;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ne Naftali abusuakuo mu: Nnipakumfoɔ dwanekɔbea kuro Kedes a ɛwɔ Galilea ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase, ne Hamot-dor ne ɛho asase, ne Kartan ne ɛho asase: Nkuro mmiɛnsa.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Gersonfoɔ nkuro nyinaa, sɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ no, ɛyɛ nkuro dummiɛnsa ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Merari mma, Lewifoɔ nkaeɛ no mmusua no, wɔmaa wɔn Sebulon abusuakuo mu: Yokneam ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase, Karta ne ɛho asase,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Dimna ne ɛho asase, ne Nahalal ne ɛho asase: Nkuro nnan;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> ne Ruben abusuakuo mu: Beser ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase, Yahas ne ɛho asase,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kedemot ne ɛho asase, Mefaat ne ɛho asase: Nkuro nnan;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> ne Gad abusuakuo mu: Nnipakumfoɔ dwanekɔbea kuro Ramot a ɛwɔ Gilead ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase, Mahanaim ne ɛho asase,",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Hesbon ne ɛho asase, Yaser ne ɛho asase: Nkuro nnan.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Merari mma mmusua ahodoɔ a wɔaka Lewifoɔ mmusua mu no nkuro nyinaa, wɔn ntonto deɛ ne nkuro dummienu.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Lewifoɔ nkuro a wɔnyaa no Israelfoɔ agyapadeɛ mu no nyinaa yɛ nkuro aduanan nwɔtwe ne ɛho mmoa adidibea nsase.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Nkuro yi mu biara wɔ mmoa adidibea nsase a atwa ho ahyia, saa na ɛteɛ nkuro yi nyinaa ho.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Na AWURADE de asase a ɔkaa ho ntam sɛ ɔde bɛma wɔn nananom no nyinaa maa Israel, na wɔdii so tenaa so.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na AWURADE maa wɔn asomdwoeɛ hyiae, sɛdeɛ ɔkaa wɔn nananom ntam no ara, na wɔn atamfoɔ nyinaa mu biara annyina wɔn anim; AWURADE de wɔn atamfoɔ no nyinaa hyɛɛ wɔn nsa.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Asɛm pa a AWURADE kaa Israel fie no nyinaa mu asɛm biara antɔ fam, ne nyinaa baa mu."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ɛnna Yosua frɛɛ Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ ne Manase abusuakuo fa no,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Mo deɛ, moadi deɛ AWURADE akoa Mose hyɛɛ mo no nyinaa so, na moatie me nne, deɛ mehyɛɛ mo no nyinaa mu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Moannya mo nuanom nna dodoɔ yi de abɛduru nnɛ da yi, na moahwɛ AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn mmara nsɛm no adi so.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na afei AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn de mo nuanom atena ase dwoodwoo, sɛdeɛ ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn no; enti monsane na monkɔ mo ntomadan mu, mo agyapadeɛ asase a AWURADE akoa Mose de maa mo Yordan agya no so.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na mo ho yie nko na monhwɛ, na monni ahyɛdeɛ ne mmara a AWURADE akoa Mose hyɛɛ mo no so, na monnɔ AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn, na monnante n’akwan nyinaa so, na mommu ne mmara nsɛm, na momfam ne ho na monsom no mo akoma nyinaa ne mo kra nyinaa mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Yosua hyiraa wɔn, na ɔgyaa wɔn kwan, na wɔsii mu kɔɔ wɔn ntomadan mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Manase abusuakuo fa no, Mose de wɔn deɛ maa wɔn Basan, na ɔfa no nso, Yosua de wɔn deɛ maa wɔn wɔn nuanom mu, Yordan agya atɔeɛ fam. Na Yosua regya wɔn kwan akɔ wɔn ntomadan mu no, ɔhyiraa wɔn,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Momfa nnoɔma bebree nsane nkɔ mo ntomadan mu, mmoa bebree pa ara ne dwetɛ ne sika ne kɔbere mfrafraeɛ ne dadeɛ ne ntoma pii pa ara, mo ne mo nuanom nkyekyɛ mo atamfoɔ asadeɛ no mu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ ne Manase abusuakuo fa no firii Israelfoɔ no nkyɛn wɔ Silo a ɛwɔ Kanaan asase soɔ sane wɔn akyiri sɛ wɔrekɔ Gilead asase so, wɔn sodie asase a wɔnam AWURADE ahyɛdeɛ a ɛnam Mose soɔ no so de maa wɔn no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na wɔduruu Yordan ho asase a ɛwɔ Kanaan asase soɔ no soɔ no, Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ ne Manase abusuakuo fa no sii afɔrebukyia hɔ wɔ Yordan ano, afɔrebukyia a wohwɛ a, ɛso.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no tee sɛ wɔse: Hwɛ, Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ ne Manase abusuakuo fa no asi afɔrebukyia wɔ Kanaan asase no anim, Yordan ho asase no so, ɔfa a ɛyɛ Israelfoɔ deɛ no so.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no teeɛ no, wɔboaboaa Israelfoɔ asafo no nyinaa ano, Silo, sɛ wɔretu wɔn so sa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no somaa Ɔsɔfoɔ Eleasa ba Pinehas maa no kɔɔ Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ ne Manase abusuakuo fa nkyɛn Gilead asase so,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na wɔde mmapɔmma du kaa ne ho, Israel mmusuakuo no mu biara mu bapɔmma baako; na wɔn mu biara yɛ ne mpanimfie ti, Israel mpempem no mu.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔduruu Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ ne Manase abusuakuo fa no nkyɛn Gilead asase so, na wɔne wɔn kasaa sɛ:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Sɛ AWURADE asafo no nyinaa seɛ nie: Fom bɛn na mode afom Israel Nyankopɔn yi sɛ nnɛ moadane mo ho afiri AWURADE akyire, na moasi afɔrebukyia afa, na moate AWURADE anim atua nnɛ yi!",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Peor mfomsoɔ a yɛnnya nnwiraa yɛn ho mfirii mu de bɛsi nnɛ yi na ɔhaw baa AWURADE asafo soɔ no nnɔɔso mma yɛn?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na mo deɛ, nnɛ moresane afiri AWURADE akyi? Na morete AWURADE anim atua nnɛ yi, ɔkyena ne bo bɛfu Israel asafo no nyinaa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Nanso sɛ mo sodie asase no ho agu fi a, ɛnneɛ montwa mmra AWURADE sodie asase a AWURADE tenabea si soɔ no so na mommɛfa asase nni so wɔ yɛn mu; na AWURADE anim atua na monnteɛ, na yɛn anim atua nso monnte, mo afɔrebukyia a mosi kaa AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn afɔrebukyia no ho mu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ɛnyɛ Sera ba Akan na ɔfom ahyiradeɛ no mu, na abufuo baa Israel asafo no nyinaa soɔ? Nso ɛnyɛ ɔno nko na ɔsɛeeɛ, ne mfomsoɔ no mu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ ne Manase abusuakuo fa no gyee so ka kyerɛɛ Israel mpempem mu atitire no sɛ:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Onyankopɔn, Tweaduampɔn AWURADE, Onyankopɔn, Tweaduampɔn AWURADE, ɔno na ɔnim, na Israel nso nhunu, yɛyɛɛ no atuateɛ mu anaa AWURADE fom mu na yɛyɛeɛ a, nnye yɛn nkwa nnɛ!",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Sɛ yɛsii afɔrebukyia sɛ yɛresane afiri AWURADE akyi anaasɛ yɛrebɔ so ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ anaa aduane afɔdeɛ anaasɛ yɛrebɔ so asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ a, ɛnneɛ AWURADE mmɛbisa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɛyɛ suro ne asɛm bi nti na yɛyɛɛ saa, ɛfiri sɛ yɛse: Ɔkyena bi mo mma bɛka akyerɛ yɛn mma sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na mo ne AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn no wɔ yɛ?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ na AWURADE de Yordan yɛɛ no yɛn ne mo Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ ntam, monni kyɛfa biara wɔ AWURADE mu; na mo mma bɛma yɛn mma agyae AWURADE suro.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Enti na yɛkaa sɛ: Momma yɛnsi afɔrebukyia mfa, ɛnyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ na ɛnyɛ okum afɔdeɛ nti,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> na mmom sɛ ɛnyɛ yɛn ne mo ne yɛn awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ a wɔbɛba yɛn akyire no ntam adanseɛ sɛ yɛde yɛn hyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne yɛn kum afɔdeɛ ne yɛn asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ bɛsom AWURADE som no n’anim, na ɔkyena bi mo mma anka ankyerɛ yɛn mma sɛ: Monni AWURADE mu kyɛfa bi!",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na yɛkaa sɛ: Na ɛba sɛ ɔkyena bi wɔka kyerɛ yɛn anaa yɛn awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ saa a, yɛbɛka sɛ: Monhwɛ AWURADE afɔrebukyia no nsɛsoɔ a yɛn agyanom yɛeɛ, ɛnyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ nti, nanso ɛnyɛ okum afɔdeɛ nti, ɛfiri sɛ ɛne yɛn ne mo ntam danseni.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Yei mpare yɛn sɛ yɛbɛte AWURADE anim atua, na yɛadane yɛn ho nnɛ afiri AWURADE akyi, na yɛasi afɔrebukyia abɔ so ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ, aduane afɔdeɛ ne okum afɔdeɛ aka AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn afɔrebukyia a ɛwɔ ne tenabea anim no ho.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na Ɔsɔfoɔ Pinehas ne asafo no mmapɔmma ne Israel mpempem atitire a wɔka ne ho no tee nsɛm a Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ ne Manasefoɔ no kaeɛ no, na ɛsɔɔ wɔn ani.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na Ɔsɔfoɔ Eleasa ba Pinehas ka kyerɛɛ Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ ne Manasefoɔ no sɛ: Ɛnnɛ na yɛahunu sɛ AWURADE wɔ yɛn mu, sɛ moamfa fom yi amfom AWURADE. Afei moayi Israelfoɔ no AWURADE nsam.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ɛnna Ɔsɔfoɔ Eleasa ba Pinehas ne mmapɔmma no sane wɔn akyiri firii Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ no nkyɛn, Gilead asase soɔ, baa Kanaan asase so Israelfoɔ no nkyɛn, na wɔbɛbɔɔ wɔn amanneɛ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na asɛm no sɔɔ Israelfoɔ no ani, na wɔhyiraa Israelfoɔ Nyankopɔn no; na wɔanka bio sɛ wɔretu wɔn so sa akɔsɛe asase a Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ te soɔ no.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na Rubenfoɔ ne Gadfoɔ no too afɔrebukyia no din: Adanseɛ, ɛfiri sɛ wɔse: Ɛyɛ yɛn ntam danseni sɛ AWURADE ne Onyankopɔn."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE maa Israel home firii wɔn atamfoɔ a wɔatwa wɔn ho ahyia nyinaa nsam akyire nna pii, na Yosua abɔ akora na wadi nna bebree no,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Yosua frɛɛ Israel nyinaa, wɔn mpanimfoɔ ne wɔn atitire ne wɔn atemmufoɔ ne wɔn ahwɛfoɔ no hyiae, na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Me deɛ, mabɔ akora, na madi nna pii.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na mo nso moahunu deɛ AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn ayɛ amanaman yi, mo anim; na AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn no, ɔno na ɔko maa mo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Monhwɛ, mede ntonto makyɛ amanaman a aka yi ne amanaman a matwitwa aguo no nyinaa mu ama mo, sɛ mo mmusuakuo nni so; ɛfiri Yordan ano kɔduru ɛpo kɛseɛ no ho awia tɔbea.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn no, ɔno na ɔbɛsunsum wɔn afiri mo anim na ɔbɛtu wɔn afiri mo anim sɛ monni wɔn asase so, sɛdeɛ AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn ka kyerɛɛ mo no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Enti monhyɛ mo ho den pa ara, na monhwɛ nyɛ deɛ wɔatwerɛ no Mose mmara nwoma mu no nyinaa, na moammane amfiri ho ankɔ nifa anaa benkum,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na moankɔ amanaman a akeka mo ho yi mu; na mommmɔ wɔn anyame din, na monnka wɔn ntam, na monnsom wɔn, na monnsɔre wɔn,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na mmom AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn ho na momfam, sɛdeɛ moayɛ de abɛduru nnɛ yi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na AWURADE atu amanaman akɛseɛ a wɔn ho yɛ den afiri mo anim, na mo deɛ, obi ntumi nnyinaa mo anim de abɛduru nnɛ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Mo mu baako bɛpamo nnipa apem, na AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn no, ɔno na ɔko ma mo, sɛdeɛ ɔka kyerɛɛ mo no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Enti monhwɛ mo ho yie, na monnɔ AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na sɛ mosane mo akyiri de mo ho kɔbata amanaman yi nkaeɛ a wɔakeka mo ho yi ho, na mo ne wɔn di ayewareɛ na mokɔ wɔn mu na wɔba mo mu a,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ɛnneɛ monhunu sɛ AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn renkɔ so ntu amanaman yi mfiri mo anim bio, na wɔbɛdanedane mo afidie ne kantankoraa ne mpire, mo mfem, ne nkasɛɛ, mo aniwa mu, akɔsi sɛ mobɛsɛe afiri asase pa yi a AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn de ama mo yi soɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na hwɛ, me deɛ, ɛnnɛ merekɔ asase sofoɔ nyinaa kwan; na monhunu mo akoma nyinaa mu ne mo kra nyinaa mu sɛ asɛm baako pɛ ntɔɔ fam, nsɛmpa a AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn kaa no wɔ mo ho no nyinaa mu, ne nyinaa aba mu ama mo, emu asɛm baako mpo antɔ fam.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na sɛdeɛ asɛmpa a AWURADE kaa mo no nyinaa aba mo soɔ no, saa ara na AWURADE bɛma asɛmmɔne nyinaa nso aba mo soɔ akɔsi sɛ ɔbɛsɛe mo afiri asase pa yi a AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn de ama mo yi soɔ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Sɛ mofom AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn apam a ɔhyɛɛ mo no, na mokɔ kɔsom anyame foforɔ na mosɔre wɔn a, ɛnneɛ AWURADE abufuo bɛdɛre atia mo, na moasɛe ntɛm afiri asase pa a ɔde ama mo no so."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Yosua boaboaa Israel mmusuakuo no nyinaa ano baa Sekem, na ɔfrɛɛ Israel mpanimfoɔ ne wɔn atitire ne wɔn atemmufoɔ ne wɔn ahwɛfoɔ no hyiae, na wɔbɛgyinaa Nyankopɔn anim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ ɔman no nyinaa sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn no seɛ nie: Asuogya na mo agyanom, Abraham agya ne Nahor agya Tera tenaeɛ firi teteete, na wɔsom anyame foforɔ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na mefaa mo agya Abraham firii asuogya, na memaa no nantee Kanaan asase nyinaa so, na memaa n’asefoɔ dɔree, na memaa no Isak.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Isak nso, memaa no Yakob ne Esau; na mede Seir bepɔ memaa Esau sɛ ɔnni so; na Yakob ne ne mma siane kɔɔ Misraim.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na mesomaa Mose ne Aaron, na mehaa Misraim, sɛdeɛ meyɛɛ no wɔ mu no, na akyire yi no meyii mo firii hɔ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na meyii mo agyanom firii Misraim no, mobaa ɛpo no ano; na Misraimfoɔ de nteaseɛnam ne apɔnkɔfoɔ tii mo agyanom baa Mmɛwa Po no ho;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na wɔsu frɛɛ AWURADE, na ɔde esum kabii too mo ne Misraimfoɔ no ntam, na ɔmaa ɛpo no baa wɔn so bɛkataa wɔn so. Na mo ani hunuu deɛ meyɛɛ Misraim, na motenaa ɛserɛ so nna pii.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na mede mo baa Amorifoɔ a wɔte Yordan agya no asase so, na wɔne mo koe, na mede wɔn mehyɛɛ mo nsa, na modii wɔn asase no so, na mesɛee wɔn firii mo anim.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɛnna Moabhene Sipor ba Balak sɔre bɛnee Israel koeɛ, na ɔsoma maa wɔkɔhyiaa Beor ba Bileam sɛ ɔmmɛdome mo;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> na mampene sɛ mɛtie Bileam, na nhyira na ɔhyiraa mo, na meyii mo ne nsam.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na motwaa Yordan baa Yeriko, na Yerikofoɔ ne mo koe ne Amorifoɔ ne Perisifoɔ ne Kanaanfoɔ ne Hetifoɔ ne Girgasifoɔ ne Hewifoɔ ne Yebusifoɔ; na mede wɔn mehyɛɛ mo nsa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na mesomaa nkotokurodu dii mo anim maa wɔpamoo wɔn firii mo anim, Amorifoɔ ahemfo baanu no, ɛnyɛ wo nkrantɛ so na ɛnyɛ wo tadua soɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na memaa mo asase a woammrɛ ho ne nkuro a woankyekyerɛ, na motenaa mu; bobe nturo ne ngodua nturo nso a moantɛ na modie yi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na afei monsuro AWURADE na monsom no mudie ne nokorɛ mu, na mompa anyame a mo agyanom som wɔ asuogya ne Misraim no, na monsom AWURADE.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na sɛ ɛnyɛ wɔ mo ani so sɛ mobɛsom AWURADE a, ɛnneɛ ɛnnɛ monyi deɛ mobɛsom no mfa, sɛ anyame a mo agyanom someeɛ a wɔwɔ asuogya no oo, sɛ Amorifoɔ a mote wɔn asase soɔ yi anyame oo, na me ne me fie deɛ, yɛbɛsom AWURADE.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔman no gyee so sɛ: Yei mpare yɛn sɛ yɛbɛgya AWURADE hɔ akɔsom anyame foforɔ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE ne yɛn Nyankopɔn, ɔno ne deɛ ɔyii yɛn ne yɛn agyanom Misraim asase soɔ firii nkoafie baeɛ, na ɔyɛɛ nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ akɛseɛ yi yɛn anim, na ɔhwɛɛ yɛn ɔkwan a yɛnam soɔ no nyinaa mu ne aman a yɛfaa wɔn mu no nyinaa mu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na AWURADE apamo aman no nyinaa ne Amorifoɔ a wɔte asase no soɔ no afiri yɛn anim; yɛn nso yɛbɛsom AWURADE, na ɔno ne yɛn Nyankopɔn.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ ɔman no sɛ: Morentumi nsom AWURADE, ɛfiri sɛ ɔyɛ Onyankopɔn kronkron, Onyankopɔn ninkufoɔ ne no, ɔremfa mo mmarato ne mo bɔne nkyɛ mo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Sɛ mogya AWURADE hɔ na mokɔsom ananafoɔ anyame a, ɔbɛdane ayɛ mo bɔne na wama moahye, sɛ ɔyɛɛ mo yie kane no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔman no ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: Dabi, na AWURADE ara na yɛbɛsom no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ ɔman no sɛ: Mo ara ne mo ho adansefoɔ sɛ mo ara moayi AWURADE afa sɛ mobɛsom no. Na wɔkaa sɛ: Adansefoɔ ne yɛn.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na afei montoto amannɔne anyame a ɛwɔ mo mu no ngu, na monnanedane mo akoma mma AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɔman no ka kyerɛɛ Yosua sɛ: AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn na yɛbɛsom no, na ne nne na yɛbɛtie.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ɛnna Yosua ne ɔman no pam da no ara, na ɔmaa wɔn ahyɛdeɛ ne atemmudeɛ wɔ Sekem.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Yosua twerɛɛ nsɛm yi hyɛɛ Nyankopɔn mmara nwoma no mu, na ɔde ɔboɔ kokuroo sii hɔ wɔ odum dua a ɛsi AWURADE kronkronbea no ase.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na Yosua ka kyerɛɛ ɔman no nyinaa sɛ: Hwɛ, ɔboɔ yi nni yɛn adanseɛ, na ɛno na ate AWURADE nsɛm a ɔne yɛn kaeɛ no nyinaa; na ɛnni mo adanseɛ, na moampa mo Nyankopɔn akyi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ɛnna Yosua gyaa ɔman no kwan maa wɔn nyinaa kokɔɔ wɔn agyapadeɛ soɔ.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na nsɛm no akyiri no, Nun ba Yosua, AWURADE akoa no wui, na wadi mfirinhyia ɔha ne du.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na wɔsiee no n’agyapadeɛ mu, Timnat-sera a ɛwɔ Efraim bepɔ soɔ wɔ Gaas bepɔ atifi fam.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na Israel som AWURADE, Yosua nna nyinaa, ne nna a mpanimfoɔ a wɔnyini kyɛree Yosua akyiri nyinaa na wɔhunuu AWURADE nnwuma a ɔyɛ maa Israel no nyinaa wɔ hɔ no.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na Yosef nnompe a Israelfoɔ de firii Misraim baeɛ no, wɔkorae wɔ Sekem, asase a Yakob tɔ firii Sekem agya, Hamor mma nsam maa nnwetɛbena ɔha no mu, na ɛyɛɛ Yosef mma agyapadeɛ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na Aaron ba Eleasa nso wui, na wɔkoraa no ne ba Pinehas kuro Gibea a wɔde maa no, Efraim bepɔ soɔ no mu."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;